<article id="index" lang="sk">
  <articleinfo>
    <title>Slovak-HOWTO</title>
    <authorgroup>
      <author>
	<firstname>Jįn</firstname><othername>'judas'</othername><surname>Tomka</surname>
      </author>
    </authorgroup>
    <releaseinfo>verzia 4 (Blanka)</releaseinfo>
    <pubdate>19. februįr 2002</pubdate>

    <keywordset>
      <keyword>Slovakia</keyword>   <keyword>Slovensko</keyword>    <keyword>sloven&ccaron;ina</keyword>
      <keyword>keyboard</keyword>   <keyword>klįvesnica</keyword>   <keyword>kbd</keyword>
      <keyword>font</keyword>       <keyword>pķsmo</keyword>        <keyword>console</keyword>
      <keyword>konzola</keyword>    <keyword>GNU</keyword>          <keyword>Linux</keyword>
    </keywordset>
  
    <abstract>
      <para>Tento document poskytuje informįcie tżkajśce sa problematiky miestnych nastavenķ v
        prostredķ opera&ccaron;nżch systémov GNU/Linux s oh&lcaron;adom na potreby slovenského u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;a.</para>
    </abstract>
  </articleinfo>

<!--DOCTYPE section PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DocBook V4.1//EN"-->
<!-- $Id$ -->

<section id="intro">
  <title>Śvodné informįcie</title>
  
  <section id="intro-licence">
    <title>Licencia</title>

    <para>Įno, mō&zcaron;ete &ccaron;ķta&tcaron; tento document, a to aj na komer&ccaron;né u&ccaron;ely!</para>

    <para>Autori nenesś zodpovednos&tcaron; za materiįlnu &ccaron;i psychickś ujmu spōsobenś &ccaron;itate&lcaron;ovi, jeho
      rodinnżm prķslu&scaron;nķkom, domįcim a hospodįrskym zvieratįm, prķpadne po&ccaron;ķta&ccaron;ovému
      zariadeniu.</para>

    <para>Toto je <quote>free</quote> document --- mō&zcaron;ete ho &scaron;ķri&tcaron; a/alebo modifikova&tcaron; v sślade s
      podmienkami licencie <citetitle><acronym>GNU</acronym> Free Documentation Licence</citetitle>,
      ktorej znenie nįjdete na adrese <ulink url="http://www.gnu.org/licenses/fdl.html">
      http://www.gnu.org/licenses/fdl.html</ulink>.</para>
  </section> <!-- intro-licence -->

  <section id="intro-contrib">
    <title>Aktuįlna verzia a prispievanie</title>

    <para>Ak nįjdete v tomto sśbore nie&ccaron;o, &ccaron;o je nezlś&ccaron;ite&lcaron;né s va&scaron;im linuxovżm presved&ccaron;enķm,
      napķ&scaron;te najskōr do diskusie linux, potom sk-i18n, dajte prķspevok na www.linux.sk a
      poohovįrajte ma na &num;sklug. V prķpade, &zcaron;e vįs to neprejde, skontrolujte, &ccaron;i mįte aktuįlnu
      verziu a, samozrejme, a&zcaron; nakoniec, dajte mi vedie&tcaron;. Adresy sś:
      <itemizedlist>
	<listitem>
	  <simpara>Aktuįlna verzia:
	    <ulink url="http://www.linuxdoc.org/HOWTO/Slovak-HOWTO/index.html">
	    http://www.linuxdoc.org/HOWTO/Slovak-HOWTO/index.html</ulink></simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara>Priania, s&tcaron;a&zcaron;nosti a ponuky na sobį&scaron;: <ulink url="mailto:judas@linux.sk">
	      judas@linux.sk</ulink>
	  </simpara>
	</listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
      </para>

      <para>Na tśto adresu sa tie&zcaron; obracajte, ak mįte nie&ccaron;o, &ccaron;o by nemalo chżba&tcaron; v
      <citetitle>Slovak-HOWTO</citetitle>.</para>

    <para>Nadįcia Pomō&zcaron; a skonaj prispela na dopķsanie &ccaron;asti o klįvesnici v iXoch sama sebe &ccaron;iastkou
      500&nbsp;000,-&nbsp;Sk, v televķzii Pomō&zcaron; a skonaj i v rovnomennom &ccaron;asopise boli zverejnené
      inzerįty, politickį strana <acronym>PAS</acronym> nekompromisne trvį na kompromise a v&scaron;etci
      pijś minerįlku <productname>Pomō&zcaron; a skonaj</productname>. Tigre, nosoro&zcaron;ce a lś&ccaron;ne konķky boli
      pokrstené, a predsa sa s kapitolou o klįvesnici v iXoch ni&ccaron; nedeje.  Mimochodom, sme
      naj&ccaron;ķtanej&scaron;ie <citetitle>Slovak-HOWTO</citetitle> na svete!</para>

    <para>Pri prispievanķ sa skśste riadi&tcaron; nasledovnżmi pravidlami:
      <itemizedlist>
	<listitem>
	  <simpara>Pre tżch, ktorķ majś vį&zcaron;ny zįujem podie&lcaron;a&tcaron; sa na pķsanķ
	    <citetitle>Slovak-HOWTO</citetitle>, je mo&zcaron;nż <acronym>CVS</acronym> prķstup priamo k
	    zdrojovżm kódom dokumentu na serveri <systemitem class="systemname">cvs.linuxdoc.org
	    </systemitem> v adresįri
	    <filename class="directory">/cvsroot/LDP/howto/docbook/Slovak-HOWTO/</filename>. Bli&zcaron;&scaron;ie
	    informįcie o zķskanķ CVS konta a webovskom rozhranķ k CVS serveru nįjdete v
	    <citetitle><acronym>LDP</acronym> Author Guide</citetitle>.
	    </simpara>
	</listitem>
	    
	<listitem>
	  <simpara>Opravy robte v&zcaron;dy vo formįte <acronym>SGML</acronym> (<acronym>DTD</acronym>
	    <application>DocBook</application>, verzia 4.0), ktorż je primįrnym formįtom pri tvorbe
	    tohto dokumentu. Je tie&zcaron; mo&zcaron;né posiela&tcaron; &ccaron;istż text. Prķspevky pķ&scaron;te, pokia&lcaron; mo&zcaron;no, s
	    diakritikou v norme <acronym>ISO-8859-2</acronym>.</simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara>Ak je to nie&ccaron;o vä&ccaron;&scaron;ie, dajte mi najskōr vedie&tcaron;, &ccaron;o chystįte, preto&zcaron;e je mo&zcaron;né,
	    &zcaron;e u&zcaron; na tom niekto makį a teda bu&dcaron; na to zabudnete, alebo to skśsite dorobi&tcaron; s danou
	    osobou. (Vzh&lcaron;adom na to, &zcaron;e zatia&lcaron; sa do tohto dokumentu dostalo asi 20 riadkov
	    cudzieho textu, zdį sa mi predchįdzajśca veta maximįlne smie&scaron;na. Ha-ha, zasmial some
	    sa...)</simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara>Va&scaron;e meno a adresa budś automaticky zverejnené spolu s va&scaron;im prķspevkom. Ak si
	    to ne&zcaron;elįte, musķte o to vżslovne po&zcaron;iada&tcaron;. Takisto, author prķspevku u&zcaron; jeho zaslanķm
	    implicitne sśhlasķ s aplikįciou licencie tohto dokumentu na &ccaron;as&tcaron;, ktorej je
	    autorom.</simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara>V <citetitle>Czech-HOWTO</citetitle> sa hovorķ: <quote>Kdy&zcaron; u&zcaron; n&ecaron;kdo podobnż
	    document &ccaron;te, d&ecaron;lį to z nutnosti a ne pro své pobavenķ.</quote> Musķme v&scaron;ak zobra&tcaron; do
	    śvahy, &zcaron;e v &Ccaron;echįch je vy&scaron;&scaron;ia &zcaron;ivotnį śrove&ncaron; a oni a&zcaron; to&lcaron;ko srandy
	    nepotrebujś...</simpara>
	</listitem>
      </itemizedlist></para>
  </section> <!-- intro-contrib -->

