<section id="locales">
  <title id="locales.title">Miestne nastavenia</title>

  <section>
    <title>Princķpy miestnych nastavenķ</title>

    <para>Podpora miestnych nastavenķ je dnes mimoriadne dōle&zcaron;itżm faktorom, ktorż charakterizuje
      jednotlivé opera&ccaron;né systémy. &Ccaron;asy, ke&dcaron; boli &lcaron;udia &scaron;tastnķ, &zcaron;e to nie&ccaron;o pķ&scaron;e, sś nenįvratne
      pre&ccaron; a pou&zcaron;ķvatelia vy&zcaron;adujś podporu svojich miestnych nastavenķ. V <acronym>GNU</acronym>
      systémoch je tįto podpora implementovanį priamo do &scaron;tandardnej kni&zcaron;nice jazyka
      <acronym>C</acronym> -- <acronym>GNU</acronym> libc. Tįto podpora je navrhnutį tak, aby
      zoh&lcaron;ad&ncaron;ovala v&scaron;etky po&zcaron;iadavky kladené na nastavenia pre akśko&lcaron;vek krajinu a akżko&lcaron;vek
      jazyk.</para>

    <section>
      <title>Ciele a prostriedky</title>

      <para>Rōzne krajiny a kultśry majś odli&scaron;né pravidlį komunikįcie. Tieto pravidlį mō&zcaron;u by&tcaron;
	malého rozsahu, napr. formįt dįtumu a &ccaron;asu, a&zcaron; po ve&lcaron;mi koplexné ako je jazyk, ktorżm
	hovoria.</para>

      <para>Internacionalizįcia softvéru znamenį programova&tcaron; ho tak, aby bol schopnż pracova&tcaron; s
	pou&zcaron;ivate&lcaron;ovżmi miestnymi nastaveniami. V <acronym>ISO</acronym> <acronym>C</acronym>
	pracuje internacionalizįcia v zmysle <firstterm>locales</firstterm>. Ka&zcaron;dé locale (miestne
	nastavenia) &scaron;pecifikuje skupinu pravidiel, jedno pravidlo pre ka&zcaron;dż u&ccaron;el. U&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron; si zvolķ
	skupinu pravidiel &scaron;pecifikovanķm locale (pomocou systémovżch premennżch).</para>

      <para>V&scaron;etky programy dedia nastavené locale v rįmci ich prostredia. Pod podmienkou, &zcaron;e
	programy sś napķsané tak, &zcaron;e akceptujś nastavené locales, mō&zcaron;u sa riadi&tcaron; pravidlami, ktoré
	uprednost&ncaron;uje pou&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;.</para>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Kategórie a ich funkcie</title>

      <para>Tįto &ccaron;as&tcaron; popisuje jednotlivé premenné, ktoré ovplyv&ncaron;ujś miestne nastavenia a ktorżmi
	sa riadia aj funkcie kni&zcaron;nice <acronym>GNU</acronym> libc.</para>

      <para>Nastavenie premennej prostredia sa robķ pomocou prķkazu shellu
	<screen>
bash$ export LC_PREMENNA=sk

tcsh$ setenv LC_PREMENNA sk
	</screen></para>
    
      <para><envar>LC_PREMENNA</envar> je jedna z nasledujścich:
	<itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
	    <para><envar>LC_COLLATE</envar> --- Triedenie re&tcaron;azcov. Nastavenķm tejto premennej
	      mo&zcaron;no prinśti&tcaron; aplikįcie, napr. <command>sort</command>, <command>ls</command> a iné,
	      aby pri porovnįvanķ re&tcaron;azcov brali do śvahy miestne rozlo&zcaron;enie jednotlivżch pķsmen v
	      abecede. Sloven&ccaron;ina mį naprķklad hne&dcaron; nieko&lcaron;ko znakov, ktoré by pri triedenķ pod&lcaron;a
	      &ccaron;ķselnej hodnoty znaku spōsobovali problémy. Slovenské nastavenia triedenia povedia
	      funkciam <function>strcoll</function> a <function>strxfrm</function>, &zcaron;e naprķklad
	      <literal>ch</literal> je jedno pķsmeno a nasleduje hne&dcaron; za <literal>h</literal> a nie
	      za <literal>c</literal>, &zcaron;e &scaron;iroké <literal>ä</literal> nasleduje za dlhżm
	      <literal>į</literal> a to zase za oby&ccaron;ajnżm <literal>a</literal>. Skśste si to na
	      prķkaze <command>sort</command>.  Zadajte pķsmenį <literal>cc ch hh</literal>, potom
	      zme&ncaron;te <envar>LC_COLLATE</envar> prķkazom
	      <screen>
bash$ export LC_COLLATE=sk

tcsh$ setenv LC_COLLATE sk
	      </screen></para>
	    
	  <para>Skśste to so <command>sort</command> znovu a porovnajte vżsledok...</para>
	  </listitem>

          <listitem>
	    <para><envar>LC_CTYPE</envar> --- Klasifikįcia a prevod znakov, multibyte. Sprįvne
	      nastavenie tejto premennej je nutné pre korektné rozli&scaron;ovanie znakov abecedy
	      jednotlivżch jazykov, ur&ccaron;enie &ccaron;ķslic, tzv. bielych znakov, prevod malżch pķsmen na
	      ve&lcaron;ké, at&dcaron;. Najvhodnej&scaron;ie je tśto premennś nenastavova&tcaron; a tżm umo&zcaron;ni&tcaron;, aby bola jej
	      hodnota prebratį od premennżch <envar>LC_ALL</envar> alebo <envar>LANG</envar>
	      (vi&dcaron; &dcaron;alej). Ak ale nechcete pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron; slovenské nastavenia, len ma&tcaron; sprįvne zobrazené
	      slovenské fonty a funk&ccaron;nś slovenskś klįvesnicu na konzole aj pod iXami, nastavte iba
	      tśto premennś.</para>

	    <warning>
	      <simpara>V&zcaron;dy si bu&dcaron;te stopercentne istķ, &zcaron;e mįte tśto premennś nastavenś (bu&dcaron; cez
		<envar>LC_ALL</envar>, <envar>LANG</envar> alebo priamo), lebo inak nemį zmysel
		&ccaron;ķta&tcaron; &dcaron;alej! Ono <quote>klasifikįcia a prevod znakov</quote> neznie nejako lįkavo,
		ale vedzte, &zcaron;e je to sakramentsky dōle&zcaron;ité pre &zcaron;ivot slovenskżch pķsmeniek vo va&scaron;om
		Linuxe!</simpara>
	    </warning>
	  </listitem>

	  <listitem>
	    <para><simplelist type="inline"><member><envar>LC_MONETARY</envar></member>
	      <member><envar>LC_NUMERIC</envar></member></simplelist> --- Formįt pe&ncaron;a&zcaron;nżch a
	      &ccaron;ķselnżch hodnōt.  Umo&zcaron;&ncaron;uje menu&tcaron; skupinu nastavenķ, ktoré sa pou&zcaron;ijś pri formįtovanķ
	      pe&ncaron;a&zcaron;nżch hodnōt alebo v&scaron;etkżch ostatnżch &ccaron;ķselnżch hodnōt. Sś to desatinnį &ccaron;iarka,
	      odde&lcaron;ova&ccaron; tisķcov, zoskupovanie &ccaron;ķslic, znamienka pre kladné a zaporné hodnoty,
	      at&dcaron;.</para>
          </listitem>

	  <listitem>
	    <para><envar>LC_TIME</envar> --- Formįtovanie dįtumu a &ccaron;asu. Nastavenia odde&lcaron;ova&ccaron;ov
	      medzi hodinami, minśtami a sekundami, nįzvy dnķ, poradie rok, mesiac a de&ncaron; v dįtume,
	      ...</para>
          </listitem>

	  <listitem>
	    <para><envar>LC_MESSAGES</envar> --- Vżber jazyka, pou&zcaron;itého u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;skżm rozhranķm na
	      preklad hlį&scaron;ok programov. Toto je presne tį premennį, ktorį prinśti aplikįcie hovori&tcaron;
	      po slovensky. Vi&dcaron; &dcaron;al&scaron;ie kapitoly.</para>
          </listitem>
	</itemizedlist>
      </para>

      <para>S prekladom hlįsenķ programov, hlavne s umiestnenķm sśborov s prelo&zcaron;enżmi re&tcaron;azcami,
	sśvisķ premennį <envar>NLSPATH</envar>. Mala by obsahova&tcaron; dvojbodkami oddelenż zoznam
	adresįrov, v ktorżch sa budś h&lcaron;ada&tcaron; <filename>.mo</filename> sśbory pre miestne nastavenia
	dané premennou <envar>LC_MESSAGES</envar>. Premennś <envar>NLSPATH</envar> je v&scaron;ak
	potrebné nastavova&tcaron; len vo vżnimo&ccaron;nżch prķpadoch, preto&zcaron;e aplikįcie h&lcaron;adajś preklady svojich
	hlįsenķ v &scaron;tandardnżch adresįroch pre tieto sśbory.</para>

      <para>Okrem tżchto premennżch bolo implementovanżch nieko&lcaron;ko &dcaron;al&scaron;ķch, ktoré zatia&lcaron; nie sś
	zdokumentované (<citetitle>The GNU C Library Reference Manual</citetitle>). Ich vżznam je
	zrejmż z nįzvu, tak&zcaron;e uvediem aj svoju dedukciu.</para>

      <itemizedlist>
	<listitem>
	  <simpara><envar>LC_PAPER</envar> --- Formįt papiera. V na&scaron;ich zemepisnżch &scaron;ķrkach sa
	    naprķklad pou&zcaron;ķva formįt <acronym>A4</acronym>, v Amerike je to
	    Letter, at&dcaron;. Pozor, tįto premennį neobsahuje priamo nįzov formįtu, ale (tak, ako v&scaron;etky
	    <envar>LC_</envar> premenné), skratku miestneho nastavenia, teda u nįs to bude
	    <constant>sk</constant>. Ak by sme chceli pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron; formįt Letter, museli by sme tśto
	    premennś nastavi&tcaron; na kód miestneho nastavenia niektorej z krajķn, ktorį pou&zcaron;ķva takżto
	    formįt, naprķklad <constant>us</constant>. V tomto prķpade je nutné nain&scaron;talova&tcaron; balķk s
	    miestnymi nastaveniami pre tśto krajinu (<application>locales-us</application>).
	    </simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara><envar>LC_NAME</envar> --- Formįt mena a priezviska. U nįs mį ka&zcaron;dż dve menį,
	    pķ&scaron;u sa v poradķ meno, priezvisko. V Rusku majś zase tri menį v poradķ meno,
	    otcovo-meno, priezvisko. V Ma&dcaron;arsku majś dve menį tak ako u nįs, ale pķ&scaron;u sa v opa&ccaron;nom
	    poradķ. O tom je tįto premennį. Asi...</simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara><envar>LC_ADDRESS</envar> --- Spōsob zįpisu adresy. Poradie ulice a popisného
	    &ccaron;ķsla domu, ZIP kód, PS&Ccaron; apod.</simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara><envar>LC_TELEPHONE</envar> --- Formįt telefónnych a faxovżch &ccaron;ķsel.  Ur&ccaron;uje
	    zoskupovanie &ccaron;ķslic, ich oddelovanie, po&ccaron;et &ccaron;ķsel predvo&lcaron;by, ...</simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara><envar>LC_MEASUREMENT</envar> --- Miery. Jednotky hmotnosti, objemu, teploty a
	    d&lacute;&zcaron;ky, pou&zcaron;ķvané v tej ktorej krajine. Program napķsanż v <acronym>USA</acronym> bude
	    pravdepodobne po&ccaron;ķta&tcaron; s galónmi vody, ale ak je sprįvne napķsanż, s premennou
	    <envar>LC_MEASUREMENT</envar> nastavenou na <quote>sk</quote> bude zobrazova&tcaron; litre v
	    sprįvnom pomere. To isté platķ naprķklad pre prevod teploty vo Fahrenheitovej stupnici
	    na stupne Celsia.</simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara><envar>LC_IDENTIFICATION</envar> --- Az apįd, tak toto neviem. Rodné &ccaron;ķslo?
	    &Ccaron;ķslo sociįlneho poistenia? &Ccaron;ķslo topįnok?</simpara>
	</listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>&Dcaron;al&scaron;ie premenné</title>
  
      <itemizedlist>
	<listitem>
	  <simpara><envar>LC_ALL</envar> --- Ak je tįto premennį nastavenį, pou&zcaron;ije sa jej hodnota
	    pre v&scaron;etky vy&scaron;&scaron;ie spomenuté skupiny locales, bez oh&lcaron;adu na hodnotu prķslu&scaron;nżch
	    premennżch.</simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara><envar>LANG</envar> --- Hodnota tejto premennej sa pou&zcaron;ije pre tie skupiny
	    locales, ktoré nemajś prķslu&scaron;nś premennś nastavenś.</simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <simpara><envar>LANGUAGE</envar> --- Alternatķvne miestne nastavenia. Tįto premennį mō&zcaron;e
	    obsahova&tcaron; usporiadanż zoznam kódov miestnych nastavenķ oddelenżch dvojbodkami. Sśbory s
	    prekladmi hlį&scaron;ok programov sa budś h&lcaron;ada&tcaron; v poradķ, v akom sś ur&ccaron;ené v tomto zozname. Ak
	    sa nepodarķ nįjs&tcaron; sśbor s prelo&zcaron;enżmi hlį&scaron;kami programu v jednom jazyku, pou&zcaron;ije sa
	    sśbor pre nasledujści jazyk v zozname <envar>LANGUAGE</envar>.  Navy&scaron;e, ak sa sśbor pre
	    prvż jazyk aj nįjde, ale niektorż re&tcaron;azec z neho nie je prelo&zcaron;enż, nepou&zcaron;ije sa pōvodnż
	    (anglickż), ale najskōr sa pokśsi nįjs&tcaron; preklad daného re&tcaron;azca v sśbore pre &dcaron;al&scaron;ķ jazyk
	    v zozname <envar>LANGUAGE</envar>.  To je vżhodné pre &lcaron;udķ, ktorķ okrem svojho jazyka
	    ovlįdajś nejakż inż lep&scaron;ie ako angli&ccaron;tinu, v ktorej sś zvy&ccaron;ajne programy originįlne
	    napķsané. Naprķklad Slovįk by mohol ma&tcaron; nastavené
	    <computeroutput>LANGUAGE="sk:cz"</computeroutput> a Szolvįk z Komįrom zase
	    <computeroutput>LANGUAGE="hu:sk"</computeroutput>.</simpara>

	  <caution>
	    <simpara>Premennį <envar>LANGUAGE</envar> ovplyv&ncaron;uje len premennś
	      <envar>LC_MESSAGES</envar>! Pre sprįvnu funkciu je nutné nastavi&tcaron; aj ostatné premenné
	      (minimįlne <envar>LC_CTYPE</envar>).</simpara>
	  </caution>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <para><envar>LINGUAS</envar> --- Tįto premennį nemį &scaron;peciįlny vżznam z h&lcaron;adiska
	    <acronym>GNU</acronym> libc, ale zvykne sa pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron; pri in&scaron;talįcii programov (zo
	    zdrojįkov). Medzerami oddelenż zoznam kódov miestnych nastavenķ ur&ccaron;uje jazyky, pre ktoré
	    si u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron; &zcaron;elį in&scaron;talova&tcaron; preklady re&tcaron;azcov aplikįcie. Prķklad:
	    <screen>
bash$ export LINGUAS="sk cz"
bash$ ./configure
bash$ make install
	    </screen></para>

	  <simpara>Tieto prķkazy skompilujś a nain&scaron;talujś aplikįciu s podporou sloven&ccaron;iny a &ccaron;e&scaron;tiny.
	    In&scaron;tala&ccaron;né skripty obvykle tie&zcaron; kontrolujś obsah premennżch <envar>LANG</envar> a
	    <envar>LC_ALL</envar>, tieto ale mō&zcaron;u obsahova&tcaron; len jeden kód miestnych
	    nastavenķ.</simpara>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <para><envar>RPM_INSTALL_LANG</envar> --- &Ccaron;astej&scaron;ie ako zo zdrojového kódu sa aplikįcie
	    in&scaron;talujś z rōznych balķkov (rpm, deb, ...). Kvōli &scaron;etreniu miestom na disku (a logike
	    -- mįlokto ovlįda tridsa&tcaron; re&ccaron;ķ) je v <acronym>RPM4</acronym> mo&zcaron;né ur&ccaron;i&tcaron; jazyk, ktorého
	    prelo&zcaron;ené hlį&scaron;ky sa budś in&scaron;talova&tcaron;. Preto odporś&ccaron;am do sśboru
	    <filename>.bash_profile</filename> (<filename>.login</filename>) u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;a, ktorż
	    in&scaron;taluje balķky (root), vlo&zcaron;i&tcaron; nasledovnż riadok:
	    <screen>
bash$ export RPM_INSTALL_LANG=sk

tcsh$ setenv RPM_INSTALL_LANG "sk"
	    </screen></para>

	  <simpara>Ak sa vįm nebodaj stane takį vec, &zcaron;e nain&scaron;talujete celż opera&ccaron;nż systém a a&zcaron;
	    potom sa dozviete o tejto premennej (tak, ako sa to stalo aj mne), skśste skript uvedenż
	    v &ccaron;asti <xref linkend="apps-rpm4" endterm="apps-rpm4.title">.</simpara>
	</listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Priorita premennżch</title>

      <para>Miestne nastavenia sa ur&ccaron;ujś zo spomenutżch premennżch, pri&ccaron;om tieto sa vyhodnocujś v
	tomto poradķ:
	<simplelist>
	  <member><envar>LANGUAGE</envar> --- ovplyv&ncaron;uje len <envar>LC_MESSAGES</envar>
	  </member>
	  <member><envar>LC_ALL</envar></member>
	  <member><envar>LC_*</envar></member>
	  <member><envar>LANG</envar></member>
	</simplelist></para>

      <para>To znamenį asi to&lcaron;ko, &zcaron;e ke&dcaron; raz nastavķte <envar>LC_ALL</envar>, jednotlivé
	premenné <envar>LC_*</envar> sa u&zcaron; neberś do śvahy. Na druhej strane, ak mįte
	naprķklad nastavené len niektoré z <envar>LC_*</envar>, ostatné sa nastavia na hodnotu
	premennej <envar>LANG</envar>.</para>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Kódy miestnych nastavenķ</title>

      <para>Premenné, ktoré ovplyv&ncaron;ujś miestne nastavenia, sa nap&lacute;&ncaron;ajś kódmi miestnych nastavenķ.
	Kódy miestnych nastavenķ sś re&tcaron;azce, ktorżch formįt sa riadi nieko&lcaron;kżmi pravidlami.
	V&scaron;eobecnż tvar je:
	<synopsis>
jazyk[_śzemie[.kódovanie]][@modifikįtor]
	</synopsis></para>
      
      <para><envar>jazyk</envar> je napr. <constant>sk</constant> pre sloven&ccaron;inu,
	<constant>cs</constant> pre &ccaron;e&scaron;tinu, <constant>hu</constant> pre ma&dcaron;ar&ccaron;inu, śzemie je
	<constant>SK</constant> pre Slovensko, <constant>CZ</constant> pre &Ccaron;eskś republiku,
	<constant>HU</constant> pre Ma&dcaron;arsko, kódovanie je <constant>ISO-8859-2</constant> pre
	v&scaron;etky stredoeurópske jazyky (je mo&zcaron;ne pou&zcaron;i&tcaron; nieko&lcaron;ko formįtov na zadanie kódovania) a
	modifikįtor slu&zcaron;i na povolenie alebo zakįzanie niektorżch funkciķ. Tie sś dané v definķciach
	miestnych nastavenķ. Naprķklad, pre Ve&lcaron;kś Britįniu je modifikįtorom re&tcaron;azec
	<constant>euro</constant> a pri jeho pou&zcaron;itķ sa ako pe&ncaron;a&zcaron;nį mena bude pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron; euro namiesto
	libry. To znamenį, &zcaron;e sa musķ pou&zcaron;i&tcaron; kódovanie <constant>iso-8859-15</constant>, ktoré
	definuje znaky euro a cent.</para>

      <para>Prķklady kódov miestnych nastavenķ (ka&zcaron;dż z tżchto re&tcaron;azcov je mo&zcaron;né priradi&tcaron; premennżm
	miestnych nastavenķ, ale naj&ccaron;astej&scaron;ie sa pou&zcaron;ķvajś len dvojpķsmenkové skratky v poslednom
	st&lacute;pci):
	<table>
	  <title>Prķklady kódov miestnych nastavenķ</title>
	  <tgroup cols="4" align="left" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
	    <tbody>
	      <row>
		<entry>sk_SK.ISO-8859-2</entry>
		<entry>sk_SK</entry>
		<entry></entry>
		<entry>sk</entry>
	      </row>
	      <row>
		<entry>cs_CZ.ISO-8859-2</entry>
		<entry>cs_CZ@-ch</entry>
		<entry>cs@-ch</entry>
		<entry>cs</entry>
	      </row>
	      <row>
		<entry>en_GB.iso8859</entry>
		<entry>en_GB</entry>
		<entry>en@euro</entry>
		<entry>en</entry>
	      </row>
	      <row>
		<entry>ja_JP.ujis</entry>
		<entry>ja_JP.EUC</entry>
		<entry>ja_JP</entry>
		<entry>ja</entry>
	      </row>
	    </tbody>
	  </tgroup>
	</table></para>

      <para>Nemali by sme zabudnś&tcaron; na dve &scaron;tandardné locales, ktoré sa pou&zcaron;ijś, ak nie sś systémové
	premenné nastavené a programy ich pou&zcaron;ķvajś do doby, kżm sa inicializuje lokalizįcia.
	Tvrdķm, &zcaron;e sa pou&zcaron;ijś obe, preto&zcaron;e momentįlne sś toto&zcaron;né, ale v budścnosti sa mō&zcaron;u v tejto
	oblasti &scaron;tandardy <acronym>ISO</acronym> <acronym>C</acronym> a <acronym>POSIX</acronym>
	odli&scaron;ova&tcaron; a potom to bude zįle&zcaron;a&tcaron; na konfigurįcii systému.
	<simplelist>
	  <member><constant>C</constant> --- nastavenia pod&lcaron;a &scaron;tandardu <acronym>ISO</acronym>
	    <acronym>C</acronym>.</member>

	  <member><constant>POSIX</constant> --- nastavenia pod&lcaron;a &scaron;tandardu
	    <acronym>POSIX</acronym>. V sś&ccaron;asnosti je to alias pre nastavenia
	    <constant>C</constant>.</member>
	</simplelist></para>
    </section>
  </section> <!-- locales-principles -->

  <section id="locales-slovakia">
    <title>Miestne nastavenia pre Slovensko</title>

    <para>V prvom rade treba nain&scaron;talova&tcaron; balķk s podporou miestnych nastavenķ, ktorż mį nįzov
      <application>locales</application> a tie&zcaron; balķk s podporou priamo pre Slovensko ---
      <application>locales-sk</application>. Ak mįte zįujem pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron; aj podporu pre nejakż inż jazyk
      (na na&scaron;om śzemķ je aktuįlna najmä &ccaron;e&scaron;tina a ma&dcaron;ar&ccaron;ina), musķte tie&zcaron; nain&scaron;talova&tcaron; balķky pre
      tieto jazyky.</para>

    <para>V druhom rade si musķte nain&scaron;talova&tcaron; balķky s podporou miestnych nastavenķ a priamo
      sloven&ccaron;iny (sś to <application>locales</application> a <application>locales-sk</application>).
      </para>

    <para>V &dcaron;al&scaron;om kroku si nezabudnite nain&scaron;talova&tcaron; balķky <application>locales</application> a
      <application>locales-sk</application>. Takisto, pre ka&zcaron;dż jazyk, ktorż sa chystįte pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron;,
      si nain&scaron;talujte balķk s podporou miestnych nastavenķ.</para>

    <para>V prķpade problémov s miestnymi nastaveniami sa dr&zcaron;te predchįdzajścich troch krokov.
      </para>

    <section>
      <title>Sśbory s miestnymi nastaveniami</title>

      <para>Prejdime sa teraz trochu po na&scaron;ich adresįroch. Prvż nav&scaron;tķvime <filename
	class="directory">/usr/share/locale/sk</filename>. Na prvż poh&lcaron;ad vidno, &zcaron;e adresįr a
	sśbory v tomto adresįri majś menį toto&zcaron;né s premennżmi, pomocou ktorżch sa nastavujś
	jednotlivé kategórie miestnych nastavenķ.  Je to preto, lebo prįve z tżchto sśborov sa
	na&ccaron;ķtajś nastavenia, ke&dcaron; je danį premennį nastavenį na hodnotu <constant>sk</constant>.
	Okrem nich tu mō&zcaron;e by&tcaron; e&scaron;te sśbor <filename>charset</filename>, ktorż obsahuje len jeden
	riadok s re&tcaron;azcom <computeroutput>iso-8859-2</computeroutput>. Ten hovorķ, aké kódovanie
	znakov sa mį pou&zcaron;i&tcaron; pre dané miestne nastavenia.</para>

      <para>V&scaron;etky sśbory v tomto adresįri sś binįrne dįta a adresįr <envar>LC_MESSAGES</envar>
	obsahuje sśbory, ktorżch menį sś toto&zcaron;né s nįzvami niektorżch balķkov nain&scaron;talovanżch na
	va&scaron;om systéme, s prķponou mo. Sś to preklady re&tcaron;azcov z jednotlivżch aplikįciķ. O nich si
	povieme neskōr. Teraz by sme mohli zisti&tcaron;, &ccaron;o vlastne obsahujś sśbory <envar>LC_*</envar>.
        </para>

      <para>Presu&ncaron;me sa do adresįra <filename class="directory">/usr/share/i18n/</filename>. Tu, v
	textovom sśbore <filename>sk_SK</filename> v podadresįri
	<filename class="directory">locales/</filename> sa kone&ccaron;ne nachįdzajś slovenské miestne
	nastavenia v &ccaron;itate&lcaron;nej (a editovate&lcaron;nej) forme. Sśbory v tomto adresįri majś presne danś
	&scaron;truktśru, ktorį je popķsanį v manuįlovej strįnke locale(5). Pre be&zcaron;ného pou&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;a nemį
	zmysel menu&tcaron; nastavenia v tomto sśbore, ke&dcaron;&zcaron;e ide o &scaron;tandardné nastavenia, ktoré sa
	pou&zcaron;ķvajś na celom Slovensku. Ale, proti Gustovi &zcaron;iadna putika! Ak sa teda rozhodnete zmeni&tcaron;
	nie&ccaron;o v tomto sśbore, musķte aktualizova&tcaron; sśbory v prvom spomķnanom adresįri
	<filename class="directory">/usr/share/locales/sk/</filename> prķkazom, ktorż śdaje v sśbore
	<filename>sk_SK</filename> skompiluje a ulo&zcaron;ķ do sśborov
	<simplelist type="inline">
	  <member><envar>LC_COLLATE</envar></member>
	  <member><envar>LC_CTYPE</envar></member>
	  <member>...</member>
	</simplelist>
	<programlisting>
sh$ localedef -i sk_SK -f ISO-8859-2 sk_SK
	</programlisting></para>
    
      <para>V podadresįri <filename class="directory">/usr/share/i18n/charmaps/</filename> sa
	nachįdzajś sśbory s popismi jednotlivżch kódovani znakov. Pre Slovensko je aktuįlny
	<filename>ISO-8859-2</filename> (&ccaron;o je aj obsah spomķnaneho sśboru
	<filename>charset</filename>).</para>
    
      <para>V adresįri <filename class="directory">/usr/share/locale/</filename> sa nachįdza sśbor
	<filename>locale.alias</filename>, ktorż definuje tzv. <firstterm>aliasy</firstterm> pre
	kódy miestnych nastavenķ. Pre sprįvnu funkciu slovenskżch miestnych nastavenķ by mal
	obsahova&tcaron; tieto dva riadky:
	<programlisting>
sk              sk_SK.ISO-8859-2
slovak          sk_SK.ISO-8859-2
	</programlisting></para>
    
      <para>To zabezpe&ccaron;ķ, &zcaron;e aj ke&dcaron; nezadįte kódovanie znakov, bude pou&zcaron;ité iso-8859-2. Druhż riadok
	mį na svedomķ to, &zcaron;e namiesto sk mo&zcaron;no zada&tcaron; slovak.</para>

      <warning>
	<simpara>Ale na aliasy typu <constant>slovak</constant> si dįvajte bacha! Niektoré
	  aplikįcie, ktoré v sśvislosti s miestnymi nastaveniami nevyu&zcaron;ķvajś slu&zcaron;by libc, toti&zcaron; na
	  aliasy ka&scaron;&lcaron;ś a zaujķmajś ich len prvé dva znaky nastavenżch premennżch. A tak sa zo
	  <constant>slovak</constant> stane <constant>sl</constant>, &ccaron;o je Slovinsko. Pozitķvne je,
	  &zcaron;e pre sloven&ccaron;inu mō&zcaron;ete nastavi&tcaron; premennś naprķklad na hodnotu
	  <constant>skaderukaskadenoha</constant>.</simpara>
      </warning>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Konfigurįcia miestnych nastavenķ</title>
    
      <para>Nastavenia internacionalizįcie sa (v <systemitem class="osname">RedHat</systemitem> a
	<systemitem class="osname">Mandrake</systemitem>) nachįdzajś v sśbore
	<filename>/etc/sysconfig/i18n</filename>. Je to ve&lcaron;mi u&zcaron;ito&ccaron;nż sśbor, ktorż si rżchlo
	ob&lcaron;śbite. Mo&zcaron;no v &ncaron;om nastavi&tcaron; v&scaron;etko, &ccaron;o sa kedy tżkalo internacionalizįcie, nįrodnżch
	fontov a rozlo&zcaron;enķ klįves.  Tento sśbor v&scaron;ak len definuje systémové premenné a zvykne sa
	vklada&tcaron; (<computeroutput>source  /etc/sysconfig/i18n</computeroutput>) do inicializa&ccaron;nżch
	skriptov.  Exportovanie premennżch (odovzdanie ostatnżm aplikįciįm) mį na starosti skript
	<filename>/etc/profile.d/lang.sh</filename> (<application>bash</application>) alebo
	<filename>/etc/profile.d/lang.csh</filename> (<application>tcsh</application>). Tento sa
	vykonį pri ka&zcaron;dom &scaron;tarte shellu, typicky je volanż z <filename>/etc/profile</filename>
	(<application>bash</application>) alebo <filename>/etc/csh.cshrc</filename>
	(<application>tcsh</application>).</para>

      <para>Sśbor <filename>/etc/sysconfig/i18n</filename> definuje nastavenia pre celż systém.
	Tieto sa pou&zcaron;ijś, ak sa nenįjde sśbor s u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;ovżmi nastaveniami. Ka&zcaron;dż u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron; si mō&zcaron;e
	ur&ccaron;i&tcaron; svoje vlastné nastavenia v sśbore <filename>.i18n</filename> v jeho domovskom
	adresįri.  Nastavenia sa v&zcaron;dy &ccaron;ķtajś len z jedného z tżchto sśborov, teda ak mį u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;
	svoj vlastnż sśbor <filename>&tilde;/.i18n</filename>, nastavenia zo sśboru
	<filename class="directory">/etc/sysconfig/i18n</filename> sa ignorujś.</para>

      <para>U&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron; si mō&zcaron;e zmeni&tcaron; nastavenia aj ru&ccaron;ne, kedyko&lcaron;vek sa mu zachce, nastavenķm
	premennżch prostredia
	<simplelist type="inline">
	  <member><envar>LC_MESSAGES</envar></member>
	  <member><envar>LANG</envar></member>
	  <member>at&dcaron;.</member>
	</simplelist></para>
	
      <para>Vypnś&tcaron; nejaké nastavenie je mo&zcaron;né prķkazom
	<screen>
sh$ unset LC_MESSAGES LANG
	</screen></para>

      <para>Tżm sa zru&scaron;ia nastavenia danżch premennżch (a pou&zcaron;ije sa &scaron;tandardné locale
	<constant>C</constant> alebo <constant>POSIX</constant>).</para>
      
      <para>Ak mįte naprķklad nastavené premenné <computeroutput>LC_ALL=sk</computeroutput> a
	<computeroutput>LC_MESSAGES=cz</computeroutput>, tak po prķkaze <computeroutput>unset
	LC_ALL</computeroutput> nebudete ma&tcaron; hlįsenia programov v angli&ccaron;tine, ale &ccaron;e&scaron;tine. Preto, ak
	chcete vypnś&tcaron; nejaké nastavenia, v&zcaron;dy musķte prķkazom unset zru&scaron;i&tcaron; nastavenia v&scaron;etkżch
	premennżch, ktoré mō&zcaron;u ovplyv&ncaron;ova&tcaron; dané miestne nastavenia.</para>

      <note>
	<title>export/setenv</title>

	<para>Neodpustķm si malś poznįmku k prķkazu <command>export</command>. Je to vstavanį
	  funkcia v&scaron;etkżch shellov kompatibilnżch s klasickżm <application>sh</application> (teda aj
	  <application>bash</application>). Pre shelly typu <application>tcsh</application> je
	  ekvivalentom prķkaz <command>setenv</command>.</para>

	<para>Je dōle&zcaron;ité uvedomi&tcaron; si, &ccaron;o presne tento prķkaz robķ s premennżmi. V dokumentįcii k
	  bashu sa hovorķ, &zcaron;e <command>export</command> ozna&ccaron;ķ premennś, aby bola odovzdanį detskżm
	  (<foreignphrase>child</foreignphrase>) procesom v rįmci prostredia
	  (<foreignphrase>environment</foreignphrase>). To znamenį asi to&lcaron;ko, &zcaron;e ke&dcaron; spustķte napr.
	  iXy z materského procesu <systemitem class="resource">bash</systemitem>, ktorż pri &scaron;tarte
	  exportoval premennś <computeroutput>LANG=sk</computeroutput>, v&scaron;etky aplikįcie v prostredķ
	  <application>X Window System</application> budś dedi&tcaron; toto nastavenie a teda (ak to sami
	  podporujś) budś fungova&tcaron; po slovensky. Ak budete chcie&tcaron; spusti&tcaron; aplikįciu bez slovenskżch
	  nastavenķ, musķte v <application>xterme</application> zada&tcaron; prķkaz <computeroutput>unset
	  LANG</computeroutput> (<computeroutput>unsetenv LANG</computeroutput> pre
	  <application>tcsh</application>), &ccaron;ķm pre v&scaron;etky detské procesy
	  <application>xtermu</application> (presnej&scaron;ie shellu, ktorż je v &ncaron;om spustenż), zru&scaron;ķte
	  nastavenie premennej <envar>LANG</envar>. Potom aplikįcie spustené priamo z tohto xtermu
	  budś fungova&tcaron; bez podpory sloven&ccaron;iny. Trochu sa s tżm pohrajte.</para>
      </note>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Nastavenie &ccaron;asovej zóny</title>

      <para>S miestnymi nastaveniami śzko sśvisķ aj nastavenie &ccaron;asovej zóny. Vedel by some o tom
	rozprįva&tcaron; celé hodiny, ale ono by to muselo by&tcaron; zlo&zcaron;itej&scaron;ie ako len nastavenie jednej
	premennej... A to takto:
	<screen>
bash$ export TZ="Europe/Bratislava"

tcsh$ setenv TZ "Europe/Bratislava"
	</screen></para>

      <para>Toto nastavenie ovplyv&ncaron;uje len &ccaron;asovż posun oproti hardverovżm hodinįm.  (Mimochodom,
	odporś&ccaron;am hardverové hodiny nastavené na greenwichskż svetovż &ccaron;as, &ccaron;ķm tie&zcaron; odpadajś
	problémy s prechodom medzi letnżm a zimnżm &ccaron;asom at&dcaron;. ale o tom sś popķsané iné sśbory.)
	Toto celé je dos&tcaron; dobrį vec, hlavne ak mate prķstup k po&ccaron;ķta&ccaron;u v inej &ccaron;asovej zóne, ale
	chcete pracova&tcaron; s &ccaron;asom v stredoeurópskej zóne. Do svojho sśboru
	<filename>.bash_profile</filename> (<filename>.login</filename> pre
	<application>tcsh</application>) vlo&zcaron;te vy&scaron;&scaron;ie uvedenż riadok.</para>
    </section>
  </section> <!-- locales-slovakia -->

  <section id="locales-examples">
    <title>Prķklady miestnych nastavenķ</title>
    
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
	<para>U&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron; je sķce zo stredného Slovenska, ale u&zcaron; ke&dcaron; s nķm bola jeho mama tehotnį,
	  pś&scaron;&tcaron;ala mu do brucha kurzy angli&ccaron;tiny. Nemį teda zmysel pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron; slovenské nastavenia, a&zcaron;
	  na krajné prķpady, napr. slovenské fonty v <application>Gimpe</application>. Darujte mu
	  sśbor <filename>.i18n</filename> s nasledovnżm obsahom (aj na takéto malé oné potrebuje
	  <application>locales-sk</application>):
	  <screen>
LC_CTYPE=sk
	  </screen></para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
	<para>U&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron; je normįlny, mį rįd svoj materinskż jazyk, ale netrįpi ho, ke&dcaron; mį polovicu
	  aplikįciķ po slovensky a polovicu po anglicky. Po &ccaron;esky via. Toto ho pote&scaron;ķ (nezabudnite
	  mu potajomky nain&scaron;talova&tcaron; aj <application>locales-cs</application>):
	  <screen>
LANGUAGE=sk:cs
LANG=sk
	  </screen></para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
	<para>U&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron; je z blķzkeho juhu, jeho ob&lcaron;śbené pleso je Balaton, v&scaron;etky hlį&scaron;ky chce po
	  ma&dcaron;arsky, ak sa inak nedį, pochopķ aj sloven&ccaron;inu. Nesmieme zabudnś&tcaron; na jeho miernu
	  schizofreniu, pri&ccaron;om jedno jeho ja potrebuje slovenské triedenie re&tcaron;azcov a druhé nevie
	  &zcaron;i&tcaron; bez formįtovania dįtumu a &ccaron;asu v &ccaron;e&scaron;tine. Nikdy sa nesmie zabudnś&tcaron; na in&scaron;talįciu
	  prekladov hlį&scaron;ok pre ma&dcaron;ar&ccaron;inu, &ccaron;e&scaron;tinu a sloven&ccaron;inu z balķkov, ktoré podporujś premennś
	  LINGUAS. Treba ho tie&zcaron; presved&ccaron;i&tcaron;, &zcaron;e in&scaron;talįcia
	  <application>locales-{sk,hu,cs}</application> nepredstavuje bezpe&ccaron;nostné riziko:
	  <screen>
LANGUAGE=hu:sk:cs
LC_COLLATE=sk
LC_TIME=cs
LANG=hu
LINGUAS="hu cs sk"
	  </screen></para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </section> <!-- locales-examples -->
</section> <!-- locales -->


<!--DOCTYPE section PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DocBook V4.1//EN"-->
<!-- $Id$ -->

<section id="console">
  <title>Nastavenia konzoly</title>

  <para>Tįto kapitola by mala &ccaron;ķtavou, pou&ccaron;nou a zįrove&ncaron; zįbavnou formou pojednįva&tcaron; o veciach medzi
    prstom a okom. Zįkladnou otįzkou nech nįm je <quote>Zmysel &zcaron;ivota, vesmķru a vōbec.</quote>
    </para>

  <section id="console-fonts">
    <title>Sloven&ccaron;ina na vżstupe textovej konzoly</title>

    <section id="console-fonts-fonts">
      <title>Fonty</title>

      <para>Ke&dcaron; zobudķte o polnoci hocikoho, kto vo svojom &zcaron;ivote videl po&ccaron;ķta&ccaron; a opżtate sa ho, ako
	rozbeha&tcaron; slovenské znaky, ur&ccaron;ite spomenie nie&ccaron;o ako fonty. Na zobrazovanie znakov na
	obrazovku -- &ccaron;i u&zcaron; v textovom alebo grafickom re&zcaron;ime -- slś&zcaron;ia skuto&ccaron;ne fonty. Fonty pre
	konzolu a programy ur&ccaron;ené na manipulįciu s nimi sa nachįdzajś v balķku
	<application>kbd</application>. Po jeho nain&scaron;talovanķ sś sśbory s fontami umiestnené v
	adresįri <filename class="directory">/usr/lib/kbd/consolefonts/</filename>.</para>

      <para>Pre nįs sś dōle&zcaron;ité najmä sśbory, ktoré majś v mene <filename>iso02</filename>,
	<filename>lat2</filename>, <filename>latin2</filename> alebo &ccaron;ķslo <filename>852</filename>.
	To nazna&ccaron;uje, &zcaron;e ide o fonty s podporou <emphasis>ISO-8859-2</emphasis>
	(<emphasis>latin2</emphasis>), prķpadne <emphasis>DOS codepage 852</emphasis>, &ccaron;o sś
	&scaron;tandardy aj pre slovenskś diakritiku.</para>
 
      <para>Pozor, pōvodnż balķk sa volį <application>kbd</application>, ale existuje jeho roz&scaron;ķrenį
	verzia, ktorį sa objavuje v distribściįch -- <application>console-tools</application>.
	Rozdiely medzi nimi sś minimįlne, pre <application>kbd</application> budeme pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron; prķkaz
	<command>setfont</command>, pre <application>console-tools</application> zase
	<command>consolechars</command>. Taktie&zcaron;, nįzvy dodįvanżch fontov sa trochu odli&scaron;ujś, tak&zcaron;e
	budem uvįdza&tcaron; ekvivalenty pre oba balķky.</para>
    </section> <!-- console-fonts-fonts -->

    <section id="console-fonts-theory">
      <title>Ako fonty fungujś</title>

      <para>Existuje nieko&lcaron;ko sśborovżch formįtov na ukladanie fontov, princķp je v&scaron;ak rovnakż --
	sśbor obsahuje 256 obrįzkov (<foreignphrase>glyphs</foreignphrase>), z ktorżch v&scaron;etky majś
	rovnakż rozmer (napr. 8x16 bodov -- ve&lcaron;kos&tcaron; fontu) a ka&zcaron;dż zobrazuje jeden znak.</para>

      <para>Aby nįm tżch 256 obrįzkov bolo na nie&ccaron;o dobrżch, je treba font zo sśboru zavies&tcaron; do
	znakového generįtora videokarty. Na to slś&zcaron;i jeden z prķkazov
	<variablelist>
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>kbd</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<cmdsynopsis>
		  <command>setfont</command>
		  <arg choice="plain"><replaceable>meno-fontu</replaceable></arg>
		</cmdsynopsis></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	  
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>console-tools</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<cmdsynopsis>
		  <command>consolechars</command>
		  <arg choice="plain">-f <replaceable>meno-fontu</replaceable></arg>
		</cmdsynopsis></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	</variablelist></para>
  
      <para><computeroutput>meno-fontu</computeroutput> mō&zcaron;e by&tcaron; absolśtna alebo relatķvna cesta k
	sśboru s fontom, alebo meno sśboru, pokia&lcaron; sa nachįdza v adresįri <filename
	class="directory">/usr/lib/kbd/consolefonts/</filename>, &ccaron;i u&zcaron; s prķponou, alebo
	bez.</para>

      <para>Pre &lcaron;ah&scaron;ie pochopenie tżch obrįzkov, skśste nahradi&tcaron;
	<computeroutput>meno-fontu</computeroutput> re&tcaron;azcom <computeroutput>t850</computeroutput> a
	sledujte vżsledok na v&scaron;etkżch virtuįlnych konzolįch.</para>

      <para>Naspä&tcaron; k &scaron;tandardnému fontu sa v&zcaron;dy dostanete jednżm z prķkazov
	<variablelist>
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>kbd</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<screen>
sh$ setfont
		</screen></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	  
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>console-tools</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<screen>
sh$ consolechars -d
		</screen></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	</variablelist></para>

      <para>&Ccaron;o sa presne deje? Program <command>setfont</command>/<command>consolechars</command>
	zavedie v&scaron;etkżch 256 obrįzkov do znakového generįtora
	<acronym>EGA</acronym>/<acronym>VGA</acronym> karty. Od tohto momentu sa na v&scaron;etkżch
	konzolįch bude znak s <acronym>ASCII</acronym> kódom napr. 65 vykreslova&tcaron; ako &scaron;esdesiaty
	piaty obrįzok z na&scaron;eho sśboru s fontom. E&scaron;te raz pripomķnam a dvakrįt pod&ccaron;iarkujem, &zcaron;e font
	je v&zcaron;dy rovnakż pre v&scaron;etky virtuįlne konzoly, na ktorżch zobrazuje znaky ten istż znakovż
	generįtor <acronym>EGA</acronym>/<acronym>VGA</acronym> karty.</para>

      <para>Dōle&zcaron;ité je uvedomi&tcaron; si, &zcaron;e interne ide naozaj len o obrįzky a tvar niektorého znaku vo
	fonte nemį ni&ccaron; spolo&ccaron;ného s jeho ASCII kódom. Ak by ste si sami vytvorili nejakż font (v
	dokumentįcii ku <application>kbd</application>/<application>console-tools</application> mįte
	informįcie o v&scaron;etkżch formįtoch), v ktorom by mal ten &scaron;esdesiaty piaty obrįzok tvar pķsmena
	<computeroutput>z</computeroutput>, po jeho natiahnutķ sa vįm bude pri zadanķ
	<keycombo><keycap>Alt</keycap><keycap>6</keycap><keycap>5</keycap></keycombo>, &ccaron;o je
	<acronym>ASCII</acronym> kód pķsmena <computeroutput>A</computeroutput>, zobrazova&tcaron; znak
	<computeroutput>z</computeroutput>. Ale ak tento znak ulo&zcaron;ķte do sśboru, v tomto sa bude
	nachįdza&tcaron; bajt s hodnotou 65, teda pķsmeno <computeroutput>A</computeroutput>.</para>
    </section> <!-- console-fonts-theory -->
    
    <section id="console-fonts-latin2">
      <title>Fonty ISO-8859-2</title>

      <para>Toto vyu&zcaron;ķva &scaron;tandard <emphasis>ISO-8859-2</emphasis> (a iné) - spolo&ccaron;né znaky s
	<acronym>ASCII</acronym> vykreslķ rovnako a znaky &scaron;pecifické pre tś ktorś abecedu
	<quote>namapuje</quote> na menej pou&zcaron;ķvané znaky <acronym>ASCII</acronym> tabu&lcaron;ky. Kam
	presne ktorį norma umiest&ncaron;uje znaky s diakritikou, nįs zaujķma&tcaron; nemusķ (pokia&lcaron; nevytvįrame
	vlastné fonty), hlavné je, &zcaron;e napr. anglickż text je nezmenenż (angli&ccaron;tina mį v&scaron;etky znaky
	spolo&ccaron;né so sloven&ccaron;inou) a slovenskż text u&zcaron; viac neobsahuje hlśpe znaky, ktoré so
	sloven&ccaron;inou nemajś ni&ccaron; spolo&ccaron;né.</para>

      <para>Slovenské (ISO-8859-2) fonty, ktoré sś sś&ccaron;as&tcaron;ou balķkov <application>kbd</application>
	a <application>console-tools</application>:
	<variablelist>
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>kbd</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>lat2-{08,10,12,14,16}, lat2a-16, iso02.{08,14,16}</para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	  
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>console-tools</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>lat2-{08,10,12,14,16}, lat2u-16, iso02.f{08,14,16}</para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	</variablelist></para>

      <para>Na zavedenie fontu pou&zcaron;ite prķkaz
	<variablelist>
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>kbd</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<screen>
sh$ setfont meno-zo-zoznamu
		</screen></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	  
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>console-tools</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<screen>
sh$ consolechars -f meno-zo-zoznamu
		</screen></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	</variablelist></para>

      <para>Odporś&ccaron;am pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron; <computeroutput>lat2a-16</computeroutput>, resp.
	<computeroutput>lat2u-16</computeroutput>. Ostatné fonty majś bezchybné zobrazovanie
	slovenskżch znakov, problém v&scaron;ak nastįva pri aplikįciįch, ktoré vyu&zcaron;ķvajś znaky na kreslenie
	rįm&ccaron;ekov (napr. <command>mc</command>).</para>

      <para>&Ccaron;o sa tżka fontov <computeroutput>iso02.*</computeroutput> z balķka
	<application>kbd</application>, treba pri nich pou&zcaron;i&tcaron; argument prķkazu
	<command>setfont</command> <computeroutput>-m latin2u.trans</computeroutput>. Tak&zcaron;e celż
	prķkaz na zavedenie niektorého z tżchto fontov je:
	<variablelist>
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>kbd</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<screen>
sh$ setfont iso02.16 -m latin2u.trans
		</screen></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	  
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>console-tools</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<screen>
sh$ consoletrans -f lat2u-16 -m iso02
		</screen></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	</variablelist></para>

      <para>V sśbore <filename>latin2u.trans</filename> (<filename>iso02.acm</filename>) sa nachįdza
	tzv. <foreignphrase>Aplication-Charset Map</foreignphrase> (<acronym>ACM</acronym>), akįsi
	prevodnį tabu&lcaron;ka, ktorį obsahuje riadok pre ka&zcaron;dż znak fontu a jeho podobu v kódovanķ
	<acronym>UTF-8</acronym>.</para>
    </section> <!-- console-fonts-latin2 --> 

    <section id="console-fonts-autoload">
      <title>Automatické zavįdzanie fontov</title>

      <para> Ak ste si na&scaron;li svoj font, ktorż chcete pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron; a ma&tcaron; ho automaticky zavedenż v&zcaron;dy pri
	&scaron;tarte, nie je ni&ccaron; &lcaron;ah&scaron;ie. Inicializa&ccaron;nż skript <filename>rc.sysinit</filename> robķ asi
	toto: skontroluje, &ccaron;i existuje sśbor <filename>/etc/sysconfig/i18n</filename> a program
	(skript) <filename>/sbin/setsysfont</filename>.  Ak įno, spustķ
	<command>setsysfont</command>. Ten na&ccaron;ķta <filename>/etc/sysinfo/i18n</filename> a pod&lcaron;a
	premennżch definovanżch v tomto sśbore prķkazom <command>consolechars</command> alebo
	<command>setfont</command> zavedie font.</para>

      <para>Tak&zcaron;e sta&ccaron;ķ nastavi&tcaron; sprįvne premenné v sśbore <filename>/etc/sysconfig/i18n</filename>
	a skript <filename>/sbin/setsysfont</filename> urobķ v&scaron;etko za nįs. Tento skript mo&zcaron;no
	spusti&tcaron; kedyko&lcaron;vek chcete zavies&tcaron; font nastavenż ako &scaron;tandardnż pre systém.</para>

      <para>Premenné v sśbore <filename>/etc/sysinit/i18n</filename> sś (pou&zcaron;ķvajte len menį sśborov
	bez cesty a bez prķpony!):
	<variablelist>
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>kbd</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<programlisting>
SYSFONT=lat2a-16
		</programlisting></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	  
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>console-tools</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<programlisting>
SYSFONT=lat2u-16
SYSFONTACM=iso02
		</programlisting></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	</variablelist></para>

      <para>Skriptķk <command>setsysfont</command> obsahujś oba balķky a kedyko&lcaron;vek mō&zcaron;ete zavies&tcaron;
	font nastavenż ako systémovż v sśbore <filename>/etc/sysinit/i18n</filename> jednoduchżm
	zadanķm
	<screen>
sh$ /sbin/setsysfont
	</screen></para>

      <para>Pod&lcaron;a toho, &ccaron;o sme si hovorili o tom, &zcaron;e pre v&scaron;etky virtuįlne konzoly mō&zcaron;e by&tcaron; nastavenż
	len jeden spolo&ccaron;nż font, nemį ve&lcaron;kż zmysel zavįdza&tcaron; nastavovanie fontu zvlį&scaron;&tcaron; pre ka&zcaron;dého
	u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;a. S tżm sśvisķ aj fakt, &zcaron;e nastavenie fontu sa vz&tcaron;ahuje k danému po&ccaron;ķta&ccaron;u, pri
	ktorom prįve sedķte a nie k tomu, ku ktorému ste pripojenķ napr. cez
	<application>ssh</application>.</para>

      <para>Predsa len si viem predstavi&tcaron; prķpad, ke&dcaron; niektorż z viacerżch pou&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;ov jedného
	po&ccaron;ķta&ccaron;a potrebuje odli&scaron;nż font. V tom prķpade mō&zcaron;e vlo&zcaron;i&tcaron; prķkaz na zavįdzanie fontov do
	svojich skriptov, ktoré vykonįva shell pri prihlįsenķ a odhlįsenķ. Pre bash by to mohlo
	vyzera&tcaron; takto:
	<variablelist>
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><filename>~/.bash_profile</filename>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<programlisting>
if tty 2>/dev/null |grep '/dev/tty[0-9]*$' &>/dev/null && ! [ -f ~/.font ]; then
	setfont -o ~/.font gr928a-8x16
fi
		</programlisting></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	  
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><filename>~/.bash_logout</filename>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<programlisting>
if tty 2>/dev/null |grep '/dev/tty[0-9]*$' &>/dev/null && [ -f ~/.font ]; then
	setfont ~/.font
	rm -f ~/.font
fi
		</programlisting></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	</variablelist></para>

      <para>Vonkoncom to nie je ideįlne rie&scaron;enie, ale svoj ś&ccaron;el splnķ (minimįlne po moment prvého
	odhlįsenia). Trochu sa s tżm pozabįvajte, aby sa font (a rozlo&zcaron;enie klįves) menilo len pri
	prvom prihlįsenķ a poslednom odhlįsenķ, tie&zcaron; setfont pod iXami nemį ve&lcaron;mi zmysel a tak... V
	Tips-HOWTO je uvedenż spōsob, ako zisti&tcaron;, na ko&lcaron;kżch virtuįlnych konzolįch je e&scaron;te u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;
	prihlįsenż.</para>

      <para>Inį&ccaron;, aby bolo jasné, toto vįm bude fungova&tcaron; len na lokįlnom stroji - zamyslite sa,
	pre&ccaron;o asi <command>setfont</command> (aj <command>loadkeys</command>) nefunguje cez
	vzdialenż terminįl a &ccaron;i by ste z toho nie&ccaron;o mali, keby to tak nebolo.</para>

      <para>Ak to s takżmto rie&scaron;enķm myslķte vį&zcaron;ne, tak skōr uva&zcaron;ujte nad modifikįciou skriptu
	<filename>/etc/profile.d/lang.sh</filename>, kde by sa kontroloval aj obsah u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;ského
	sśboru <filename>~/.i18n</filename> a pod&lcaron;a toho by sa zaviedol skript, popis rozlo&zcaron;enia
	klįves, prķpadne nejaké premenné...</para>
    </section> <!-- console-fonts-autoload -->
  </section> <!-- console-fonts -->

  <section id="console-kbd">
    <title>Slovenskį klįvesnica na textovej konzole</title>

    <para>Ke&dcaron; je slovenskż font na konzole rozbehanż a na&scaron;e nįrodné znaky sa zobrazujś sprįvne, mįme
      so sloven&ccaron;inou problém &ccaron;ķslo dva - ako tam tie znaky dosta&tcaron;? Keby ste si chceli tento sśbor
      len pre&ccaron;ķta&tcaron; bez potreby nįslednej nav&scaron;tevy psychiatra, sta&ccaron;ilo by zavies&tcaron; nejakż font so
      slovenskou podporou. Ale ke&dcaron;&zcaron;e ste uvedomelż linuxįk&nbsp;/&nbsp;uvedomelį linuxį&ccaron;ka, hne&dcaron;
      chcete do <citetitle>Slovak-HOWTO</citetitle> prispie&tcaron; a pomocou klįvesnice pķsa&tcaron; slovenskż
      text. Na to potrebujete s tou klįvesnicou nie&ccaron;o urobi&tcaron;.</para>

    <section id="console-kbd-kmap">
      <title>Popis rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves (keymap)</title>

      <para>Adresįre <filename class="directory">/usr/lib/kbd/keymaps/i386/qwertz/</filename> a
	<filename class="directory">qwerty/</filename> obsahujś
	po nain&scaron;talovanķ balķka
	<application>kbd</application>/<application>console-tools</application> aj popisy
	slovenského rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves. Pre nįs sś zaujķmavé sśbory
	<simplelist>
	  <member><filename>sk-prog-qwerty.map.gz</filename></member>
	  <member><filename>sk-qwerty.map.gz</filename></member>
	  <member><filename>sk-prog-qwertz.map.gz</filename></member>
	  <member><filename>sk-qwertz.map.gz</filename></member>
	</simplelist></para>

      <para>Tieto sśbory obsahujś definķcie rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves pre slovenskż jazyk, pri&ccaron;om rozdiely
	medzi nimi sś v umiestnenķ klįves <keycap>Y</keycap> a <keycap>Z</keycap> a po&ccaron;te
	slovenskżch znakov, ktoré pomocou nich mo&zcaron;no napķsa&tcaron; priamo (bez m&racute;tvych klįves). Najviac sa
	na slovenskż pķsacķ stroj podobį <computeroutput>sk-qwertz</computeroutput>, najmen&scaron;ie zmeny
	oproti americkej klįvesnici sś zase v <computeroutput>sk-prog-qwerty</computeroutput>.
        </para>

      <para>Sśbory v adresįri <filename class="directory">/usr/lib/kbd/keymaps/i386/include/
	</filename> obsahujś popis zįkladnżch rozlo&zcaron;enķ klįves (<computeroutput>azerty
        </computeroutput>, <computeroutput>qwerty</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>qwertz
	</computeroutput>), prķdavnżch klįves (<computeroutput>keypad</computeroutput>,
	<computeroutput>windowkeys</computeroutput>), prķpadne problémovżch klįves (<computeroutput>
	delete</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>backspace</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>ctrl
	</computeroutput>). Sśbory <filename>linux-*.inc.gz</filename> sś &scaron;pecifické pre linux
	(teda nie pre jazyk). Sś to napr. k&lcaron;ś&ccaron;e (<keycap>F1</keycap>-<keycap>F12</keycap>,
	kombinovanķm s <keycap>Ctrl</keycap> a <keycap>Shift</keycap> a&zcaron; po <keycap>F48</keycap>),
	<keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap> <keycap>PgUp</keycap></keycombo> a <keycombo><keycap>Shift
	</keycap> <keycap>PgDown</keycap></keycombo>, at&dcaron;.</para>

      <para>Keymapy <filename>*.inc.gz</filename> nepopisujś kompletné rozlo&zcaron;enie klįvesnice, ale
	len niektorżch jej &ccaron;astķ. Vyu&zcaron;ķvajś sa pri pripįjanķ
	(<foreignphrase>include</foreignphrase>) zo sśborov <filename>*.map.gz</filename>, &ccaron;o je
	vżhodné z dōvodu jednoduch&scaron;ej konfigurįcie klįvesnice. Naprķklad zmenou jedného riadku v
	sśbore s rozlo&zcaron;enķm <computeroutput>sk-qwerty</computeroutput> mō&zcaron;me dosta&tcaron; rozlo&zcaron;enie
	qwertz, prķpadne (to asi vyu&zcaron;ijete) jednoducho odstavi&tcaron; znaky <keycap>euro</keycap> a
	<keycap>cent</keycap>, ktoré (zatia&lcaron;?) nepotrebujeme a zbyto&ccaron;ne nįm zaberajś znaky
	<keycap>E</keycap> a <keycap>C</keycap>.</para>

      <para>Na zavedenie sśboru s popisom rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves slś&zcaron;i nasledovnż prķkaz:
	<cmdsynopsis>
	  <command>loadkeys</command>
	  <arg choice="plain"><replaceable>nazov</replaceable></arg>
	</cmdsynopsis>
	kde <computeroutput>nazov</computeroutput> mō&zcaron;e by&tcaron; absolśtna alebo relatķvna cesta ku
	keymap sśboru, alebo meno sśboru, pokia&lcaron; sa nachįdza v adresįri <filename class="directory">
	/usr/lib/kbd/keymaps/</filename>, &ccaron;i u&zcaron; s prķponou, alebo bez.</para>

      <para>&Scaron;tandardné slovenské popisy rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves nįjdeme vo vy&scaron;&scaron;ie spomķnanżch
	<filename>*.map.gz</filename> sśboroch. Ak sa chcete vrįti&tcaron; k &scaron;tandardnému rozlo&zcaron;eniu,
	prķkaz
	<screen>
sh$ loadkeys -d
	</screen>
	zavedie pōvodné, ktoré je ulo&zcaron;ené v sśbore <filename>defkeymap.map.gz</filename> niekde
	medzi ostatnżmi keymap sśbormi. Predtżm ale nikdy nezabudnite zmeni&tcaron; re&zcaron;im slovenskej
	klįvesnice na <acronym>US</acronym> znaky, tzn.  <keycap>1</keycap> dįva
	<computeroutput>1</computeroutput> a nie <computeroutput>+</computeroutput> at&dcaron;. Ak by ste
	predsa zabudli, je mo&zcaron;né, &zcaron;e klįvesy, kde sa nachįdzali slovenské znaky, nebudś fungova&tcaron;
	sprįvne (v skuto&ccaron;nosti budś fungova&tcaron; sprįvne, ale vįm sa to nebude pį&ccaron;i&tcaron;). Vtedy znovu
	zave&dcaron;te predchadzįjścu keymapu (na nefunk&ccaron;né klįvesy pou&zcaron;ite <keycap>AltGr</keycap> - pravż
	<keycap>Alt</keycap>) a klįvesou <keycap>Pause/Break</keycap> v&scaron;etko napravķte. Potom mō&zcaron;ete
	znova zavies&tcaron; defkeymap.</para>

      <para>Pokia&lcaron; sa vįm nepį&ccaron;i ani jeden zo &scaron;tandardnżch keymap sśborov pre sloven&ccaron;inu, &ccaron;o je
	pravdepodobné v&dcaron;aka riadku
	<programlisting>
include "euro"
	</programlisting>
	v include sśboroch <filename>qwerty-layout.inc.gz</filename> aj
	<filename>qwertz-layout.inc.gz</filename>, mō&zcaron;ete k&lcaron;udne pozmeni&tcaron; existujści sśbor s popisom
	rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves, prķpadne vytvori&tcaron; novż. Nebojte sa, je to zlo&zcaron;ité! Nebudem to tu
	rozpisova&tcaron; v&scaron;etko, prezrite si zopįr kmap sśborov, pre&ccaron;ķtajte manuįlovś strįnku keymaps(5) a
	mali by ste to &lcaron;ahko pochopi&tcaron;.</para>

      <para>My si povieme len o zįkladnżch veciach, ktoré nįm pomō&zcaron;u pozmeni&tcaron; existujśce kmap sśbory
	s popismi slovenskżch klįvesnķc, aby ste si poradili s (mne znįmymi) komplikįciami, alebo
	upravili rozlo&zcaron;enie klįves pod&lcaron;a svojho gusta.</para>
    </section> <!-- console-kbd-kmap -->

    <section id="console-kbd-include">
      <title>Include a nesprįvna funkcia klįves <keycap>E</keycap> a <keycap>C</keycap></title>

      <para>Problém s <keycap>E</keycap> a <keycap>C</keycap> je spōsobenż zavedenķm jednotnej meny
	v európskej śnii. Na vine nie je ani tak <acronym>EU</acronym>, ale niekto, kto symboly pre
	<keycap>euro</keycap> a <keycap>cent</keycap> umiestnil na <keycombo><keycap>AltGr</keycap>
	<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> a <keycombo><keycap>AltGr</keycap><keycap>C</keycap>
	</keycombo>, &ccaron;o sś na&scaron;e oby&ccaron;ajné <keycap>E</keycap> a <keycap>C</keycap>. Toti&zcaron;, nįrodné
	klįvesnice sś vä&ccaron;&scaron;inou rie&scaron;ené tak, &zcaron;e po zavedenķ sśboru na&dcaron;alej funguje americké
	rozlo&zcaron;enie a na prepķnanie do nįrodného re&zcaron;imu sa pou&zcaron;ķva klįvesa <keycap>Pause</keycap>,
	alebo mō&zcaron;me zadįva&tcaron; nįrodné klįvesy pri sś&ccaron;asnom dr&zcaron;anķ klįvesy <keycap>AltGr</keycap>
	(pravż <keycap>Alt</keycap>). Sśbor <filename>euro.inc</filename>, ktorż definuje tieto dva
	problémové symboly, je pripojenż zo sśboru <filename>qwerty-layout.inc</filename>, ktorż
	zase pripįjajś samotné slovenské keymapy (<filename>sk-qwerty</filename>,
	<filename>sk-prog-qwertz</filename>, &hellip;).</para>

      <para>Rie&scaron;enie je ve&lcaron;mi jednoduché - zeditujete <filename>qwerty-layout.inc</filename> (alebo
	<filename>qwertz-layout.inc</filename>) a odkomentujete znakom
	<computeroutput>&num;</computeroutput> riadok
	<programlisting>
include "euro"
	</programlisting></para>
    </section> <!-- console-kbd-include -->
  
    <section id="console-kbd-keycode">
      <title>Keycode a definovanie klįves</title>

      <para>Predchįdzajści problém s eurom mo&zcaron;no vyrie&scaron;i&tcaron; aj definovanķm znakov <keycap>E</keycap> a
	<keycap>C</keycap> v samotnom sśbore <filename>sk-qwerty.kmap.gz</filename> (alebo inom,
	ktorż pou&zcaron;ķvate) pomocou slova <computeroutput>keycode</computeroutput>:
	<programlisting>
keycode 18 = e
keycode 46 = c
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>V keymap sśboroch je pre ka&zcaron;dś klįvesu (alebo aspo&ncaron; pre ka&zcaron;dś, ktorś chceme
	predefinova&tcaron;) jeden riadok pribli&zcaron;ne tohto razenia:
	<programlisting>
keycode 3 = two at lcaron two nul nul nul nul Meta_two Meta_two...
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>&Ccaron;ķslo za <computeroutput>keycode</computeroutput> ozna&ccaron;uje ur&ccaron;itś klįvesu a re&tcaron;azce za
	<computeroutput>=</computeroutput> hovoria o tom, akż znak mį ovlįda&ccaron; klįvesnice generova&tcaron;
	pri stla&ccaron;enķ tejto klįvesy, a to bu&dcaron; samotnej, alebo v kombinįcii so &scaron;peciįlnymi klįvesmi
	<keycap>Shift</keycap>, <keycap>AltGr</keycap>, <keycap>Control</keycap>,
	<keycap>Alt</keycap>, <keycap>ShiftL</keycap>, <keycap>ShiftR</keycap>,
	<keycap>Ctrl</keycap> a <keycap>CtrlR</keycap>. To nįm dįva 256 mo&zcaron;nżch znakov na ka&zcaron;dś
	klįvesu.</para>

      <para>Vä&ccaron;&scaron;inou sa pozme&ncaron;uje len prvżch 16 kombinįciķ modifikįtorov. To je vżznam riadku
	<programlisting>
keymaps 0-15
	</programlisting>
	na za&ccaron;iatku kmap sśborov.</para>

      <para>V nasledujścom zozname je tżchto 16 kombinįciķ (po riadkoch):
	<simplelist columns="4" type="horiz">
	  <member>&zcaron;iadny</member>
	  <member><keycap>Shift</keycap></member>
	  <member><keycap>AltGr</keycap></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>AltGr</keycap></keycombo></member>
	  <member><keycap>Control</keycap></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>Control</keycap></keycombo></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>AltGr</keycap><keycap>Control</keycap></keycombo></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>AltGr</keycap><keycap>Control</keycap>
	    </keycombo></member>
	  <member><keycap>Alt</keycap></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>Alt</keycap></keycombo></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>AltGr</keycap><keycap>Alt</keycap></keycombo></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>AltGr</keycap><keycap>Alt</keycap>
	    </keycombo></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>Control</keycap><keycap>Alt</keycap></keycombo></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>Control</keycap><keycap>Alt</keycap>
	    </keycombo></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>AltGr</keycap><keycap>Control</keycap><keycap>Alt</keycap>
	    </keycombo></member>
	  <member><keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>AltGr</keycap><keycap>Control</keycap>
	    <keycap>Alt</keycap></keycombo></member>
        </simplelist></para>
	  
      <para>Z h&lcaron;adiska slovenskej klįvesnice sś dōle&zcaron;ité len prvé &scaron;tyri - prvé dva sś zvy&ccaron;ajne
	nezmenené americké znaky, napr. <computeroutput>two at</computeroutput>, &ccaron;o je
	<keycap>2</keycap> <keycap>@</keycap>, a druhé dva sś znaky slovenskej abecedy, ktoré bude
	ovlįda&ccaron; klįvesnice posiela&tcaron; aplikįciįm ak pri stla&ccaron;enķ tejto klįvesy budeme sś&ccaron;asne dr&zcaron;a&tcaron;
	klįvesu <keycap>AltGr</keycap> (pravż <keycap>Alt</keycap>), napr.  <computeroutput>lcaron
	two</computeroutput>, &ccaron;o je na&scaron;e <keycap>&lcaron;</keycap> <keycap>2</keycap>.</para>

      <para>Aby ste mohli vklada&tcaron; slovenské znaky, nemusķte celż &ccaron;as pridr&zcaron;iava&tcaron;
	<keycap>AltGr</keycap> nosom, ale mō&zcaron;ete pou&zcaron;i&tcaron; <keycap>Pause/Break</keycap>, ktorż v
	kontexte s nįrodnżmi klįvesnicami funguje ako <keycap>AltGr Lock</keycap>. Chįpte to tak, &zcaron;e
	ke&dcaron; sa prepnete do slovenského re&zcaron;imu stla&ccaron;enķm <keycap>Pause/Break</keycap>, prvé a druhé
	dva re&tcaron;azce v ka&zcaron;dom riadku keycode sa vymenia, napr.
	<programlisting>
two at lcaron two -> lcaron two two at
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Vtedy mō&zcaron;ete pou&zcaron;i&tcaron; <keycap>AltGr</keycap> na zadįvanie znakov americkej klįvesnice,
	alebo sa opätovnżm stla&ccaron;enķm <keycap>Pause/Break</keycap> prepnś&tcaron; spät do
	<acronym>US</acronym> re&zcaron;imu.</para>

      <para>Riadok pre klįvesu s kódom 41 (znaky <keycap>`</keycap> a <keycap>~</keycap>), mį v
	sśbore <filename>sk-qwerty.map.gz</filename> nasledovnż tvar:
	<programlisting>
keycode 41 = grave asciitilde dead_diaeresis dead_circumflex ...
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Mne osobne sa nepį&ccaron;i, &zcaron;e sś tu umiestnené m&racute;tve klįvesy <keycap>dead_diaeresis</keycap>
	(dve bodky nad znakom) a <keycap>dead_circumflex</keycap> (mäk&ccaron;e&ncaron;), preto&zcaron;e ich nepotrebujem
	--- <keycap>ä</keycap> aj <keycap>ō</keycap> na slovenskej klįvesnici predsa je. A keby aj
	nebolo, na ich pķsanie mō&zcaron;em k&lcaron;udne pou&zcaron;i&tcaron; m&racute;tvy klįves mäk&ccaron;e&ncaron;. O tom si bli&zcaron;&scaron;ie povieme v
	&ccaron;asti o compose sekvenciįch. Teraz chcem ma&tcaron; na tomto mieste znaky <keycap>;</keycap>
	(semicolon) a <keycap>°</keycap> (degree) tak, ako je to na popiske mojej klįvesnice. Zmenķm
	teda riadok takto:
	<programlisting>
keycode 41 = grave asciitilde semicolon degree ...
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Inį&ccaron;, ten stupe&ncaron; asi nie je stupe&ncaron;, ale m&racute;tvy znak krś&zcaron;ku nad pķsmenom, napr. v &ccaron;e&scaron;tine
	nad u, ale takż klįves je nįm fakt nani&ccaron;. Rad&scaron;ej budeme pķsa&tcaron; stupne.</para>

      <para>Nįzvy znakov, ktoré sa pou&zcaron;ķvajś pri definovanķ jednotlivżch klįves si mō&zcaron;ete pre znaky
	<acronym>ASCII</acronym> zisti&tcaron; v sśbore <filename>us.map.gz</filename>. &Ccaron;ķselné kódy
	v&scaron;etkżch klįves vįm vyp&lcaron;uje program
	<cmdsynopsis>
	  <command>showkey</command>
	</cmdsynopsis></para>

      <para>Pravidlį pre nįzvy znakov &scaron;pecifickżch pre sloven&ccaron;inu v kmap sśboroch:
	<orderedlist>
	  <listitem>
	    <para>Prvé pķsmeno v nįzve ur&ccaron;uje <acronym>ASCII</acronym> znak, pre ktorż chceme pou&zcaron;i&tcaron;
	      diakritiku.</para>
	  </listitem>

	  <listitem>
	    <para>K nemu pridįme identifikįtor diakritického znamienka:
	      <simplelist>
		<member>caron --- mäk&ccaron;e&ncaron;</member>
		<member>acute --- d&lacute;&zcaron;e&ncaron;</member>
		<member>diaeresis --- dve bodky nad</member>
		<member>circumflex --- vokį&ncaron;</member>
	      </simplelist></para>

	    <para>Naprķklad:
	      <simplelist>
		<member>scaron = <keycap>&scaron;</keycap></member>
		<member>uacute = <keycap>ś</keycap></member>
		<member>Ocircumflex = <keycap>Ō</keycap></member>
	      </simplelist></para>
	  </listitem>
	</orderedlist></para>
	      
      <para>Nįzvy &dcaron;al&scaron;ķch znakov &scaron;pecifickżch pre sloven&ccaron;inu:
	<simplelist>
	  <member>0xa7 --- <keycap>§</keycap> (paragraf)</member>
	  <member>degree --- <keycap>°</keycap> stupe&ncaron;</member>
	</simplelist></para>
	  
      <para>Pre sprįvnu interpretįciu identifikįtorov znakov s diakritikou je nutné na za&ccaron;iatku kmap
	sśboru ur&ccaron;i&tcaron; kódovś strįnku, pre ktorś bude ur&ccaron;enż tento popis rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves. Ide o to,
	&zcaron;e ten istż znak mō&zcaron;e ma&tcaron; v rōznych kódovżch strįnkach inż <acronym>ASCII</acronym> kód.
	Implicitnį hodnota je <constant>iso-8859-1</constant>, teda pre slovenské keymapy je nutné
	vlo&zcaron;i&tcaron; riadok:
	<programlisting>
charset "iso-8859-2"
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>E&scaron;te jeden prķklad: ak chcete pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron; slovenské rozlo&zcaron;enie
	<computeroutput>qwertz</computeroutput> a americké rozlo&zcaron;enie
	<computeroutput>qwerty</computeroutput>, potrebujete vymeni&tcaron; znaky <keycap>Y</keycap> a
	<keycap>Z</keycap>:
	<programlisting>
keycode 21 = y Y z Z
keycode 44 = z Z y Y
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Na prvż poh&lcaron;ad to mō&zcaron;e fungova&tcaron; dobre, ale problém sa prejavķ pri zapnutom <keycap>Caps
	Lock</keycap> - znaky <keycap>Y</keycap> a <keycap>Z</keycap> sa stįle pķ&scaron;u malżmi
	pķsmenami. Pri pķsanķ popisov rozlo&zcaron;enķ znakov mo&zcaron;no takżto problém o&scaron;etri&tcaron; pridanķm pķsmena
	<computeroutput>+</computeroutput> pred ka&zcaron;dé pķsmeno v keycode riadku danej klįvesy.
	Pķsmeno <computeroutput>+</computeroutput> ur&ccaron;uje nasledovnému pķsmenu atribśt
	<foreignphrase>letter</foreignphrase>, teda sa bude pri stla&ccaron;enom <keycap>Caps Lock</keycap>
	pķsa&tcaron; ve&lcaron;ké pķsmeno. V&scaron;etky pķsmenį <keycap>a</keycap>-<keycap>z</keycap>,
	<keycap>A</keycap>-<keycap>Z</keycap> majś tento atribśt priradenż automaticky, ale to len v
	prķpade, &zcaron;e majś keycode riadok tvaru:
	<programlisting>
keycode 21 = y
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>V na&scaron;om prķpade teda musķme priradi&tcaron; tento atribśt v&scaron;etkżm znakom explicitne.  Tak&zcaron;e,
	kone&ccaron;nį śprava keymapy bude:
	<programlisting>
keycode 21 = +y +Y +z +Z
keycode 44 = +z +Z +y +Y
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Pre vżmenu pķsmen toto rie&scaron;enie funguje spo&lcaron;ahlivo, bohu&zcaron;ia&lcaron;, e&scaron;te stįle neexistuje
	spōsob, ktorżm by sa dalo dosiahnu&tcaron; naprķklad pķsanie ve&lcaron;kżch pķsmen s diakritikou pri
	zapnutom <keycap>Caps Lock</keycap> jednoduchżm stlį&ccaron;anķm ich klįves, ako je to v slovenskom
	popise rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves pre <application>X Window System</application>.</para>

    </section> <!-- console-kbd-keycode -->
    
    <section id="console-kbd-dead">
      <title>M&racute;tve klįvesy a sekvencie compose</title>

      <para>S m&racute;tvymi klįvesami sśvisia v kmap sśboroch riadky tvaru
	<programlisting>
compose 'c1' 'c2' to 'c3'
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Predstavme si m&racute;tve znaky ako śplne oby&ccaron;ajné znaky s tżm rozdielom, &zcaron;e ovlįda&ccaron;
	klįvesnice ich neposiela aplikįciįm, ale zostanś niekde <quote>visie&tcaron;</quote>, kżm z
	klįvesnice neprķde &dcaron;al&scaron;ķ znak. Ovlįda&ccaron; klįvesnice nepo&scaron;le ani tento, ale pokśsi sa spoji&tcaron; ho
	s predchįdzajścim m&racute;tvym znakom a a&zcaron; vżsledok spojenia pustķ &dcaron;alej. No, a ako mį to spojenie
	uskuto&ccaron;ni&tcaron;, to mu presne hovoria riadky <computeroutput>compose</computeroutput> v keymap
	sśboroch.</para>

      <para>V nasledujścej tabu&lcaron;ke je zoznam m&racute;tvych znakov pou&zcaron;ķvanżch v sloven&ccaron;ine, spolu s
	vżznamom a znakom, ktorżm sa ozna&ccaron;ujś v compose sekvenciįch.
	<table id="console-kbd-dead.tables.dead">
	  <title id="console-kbd-dead.tables.dead.title">M&racute;tve klįvesy</title>
	  <tgroup cols="3">
	    <thead>
	      <row>
		<entry>Nįzov</entry>
		<entry>Vżznam</entry>
		<entry>Compose</entry>
	      </row>
	    </thead>

	    <tbody>
	      <row>
		<entry>dead_acute</entry>
		<entry>d&lacute;&zcaron;e&ncaron;</entry>
		<entry>\'</entry>
	      </row>

	      <row>
		<entry>dead_circumflex</entry>
		<entry>mäk&ccaron;e&ncaron;</entry>
		<entry>^</entry>
	      </row>

	      <row>
		<entry>dead_diaeresis</entry>
		<entry>dve bodky nad</entry>
		<entry>"</entry>
	      </row>
	    </tbody>
	  </tgroup>
	</table></para>

      <procedure>
	<title>Postup pri pķsani compose sekvenciķ</title>
	
	<step>
	  <para>Ka&zcaron;dį compose sekvencia sa za&ccaron;ķna k&lcaron;ś&ccaron;ovżm slovom
	    <computeroutput>compose</computeroutput>.</para>
	</step>

	<step>
	  <para>Nasleduje compose znak m&racute;tvej klįvesy (pod&lcaron;a tabu&lcaron;ky <xref
	    linkend="console-kbd-dead.tables.dead" endterm="console-kbd-dead.tables.dead.title">),
	    naprķklad <computeroutput>\'</computeroutput>.
	  </para>

	  <para>Druhż je znak, s ktorżm chceme m&racute;tvu klįvesu kombinova&tcaron;, naprķklad
	    <computeroutput>A</computeroutput>.</para>

	  <para>Za k&lcaron;ś&ccaron;ovżm slovom <computeroutput>to</computeroutput> nasleduje vżsledok spojenia
	    m&racute;tvej klįvesy a znaku bez diakritiky, teda <computeroutput>Į</computeroutput>.</para>
	</step>
      </procedure>

      <para>Je praktické ma&tcaron; pri vytvįranķ compose sekvenciķ zavedenż slovenskż font, aby ste
	vżsledok mohli hne&dcaron; kontrolova&tcaron;. Ve&lcaron;kou pomocou je tie&zcaron; mo&zcaron;nos&tcaron; prķkazu
	<command>loadkeys</command> &ccaron;ķta&tcaron; zo &scaron;tandardného vstupu. Naprķklad:
	<screen>
sh$ loadkeys
include "/usr/lib/kbd/keymaps/i386/include/windowkeys.map.gz"
keycode 41 = grave asciitilde semicolon dead_diaeresis
compose '"' 'a' to 'ä'
# ukon&ccaron;enie zadįvania:  EOF  -  Ctrl-D
sh$
	</screen></para>
	
      <para>Popis aktuįlneho rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves mō&zcaron;ete ulo&zcaron;i&tcaron; do sśboru prķkazom
	<screen>
sh$ dumpkeys > subor
	</screen></para>
	
      <para>Ak nemįte zavedenż slovenskż popis rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves, musķte zadįva&tcaron; tieto znaky ako
	<keycap>Alt</keycap> sekvencie, poprķpade vklada&tcaron; ich hex kódy v tvare
	<keycode>0xed</keycode> pre <keycap>ķ</keycap>. Vżpis znakov aktuįlneho fontu spolu s ich
	hex kódmi vįm urobķ program
	<variablelist>
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>kbd</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<cmdsynopsis>
		  <command>showfont</command>
		</cmdsynopsis></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	  
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><application>console-tools</application>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<cmdsynopsis>
		  <command>showcfont</command>
		</cmdsynopsis></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	</variablelist></para>

      <para>E&scaron;te raz na&scaron;a compose sekvencia a nejaké navy&scaron;e:
	<programlisting>
compose '\'' 'A' to 'Į'   # dlhé A cez d&lacute;&zcaron;e&ncaron;
compose '^'  'O' to 'Ō'   # O s vokį&ncaron;om cez mäk&ccaron;e&ncaron;
compose '^'  'a' to 'ä'   # &scaron;iroké a cez mäk&ccaron;e&ncaron;,
compose '^'  'A' to 0x84  # ...preto nepotrebujeme dead_diaeresis
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Mimochodom, v sśbore <filename>/usr/lib/kbd/keymaps/compose/compose.latin2</filename>
	mįte zoznam compose sekvenciķ pre normu <acronym>ISO-8859-2</acronym>.</para>
    </section> <!-- console-kbd-dead -->

    <section id="console-kbd-autoload">
      <title>Automatické zavįdzanie keymap sśboru</title>

      <para>Na nastavenie rozlo&zcaron;enia klįvesnice, ktoré chceme zavies&tcaron; pri &scaron;tarte systému, nįm slś&zcaron;i
	sśbor <filename>/etc/sysconfig/keyboard</filename>. Pre Slovįka ako repa by mal vyzera&tcaron;
	minimįlne takto:
	<programlisting>
KEYTABLE=sk-qwerty     # zavedie rozlo&zcaron;enie klįves sk-qwerty
KBCHARSET=iso-8859-2   # ...a spomķnanż sśbor compose.latin2
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Nastavenie klįvesnice pri &scaron;tarte mį na starosti skript <command>keytable</command>,
	ktorż je volanż priamo z <filename>rc.sysinit</filename>, tak&zcaron;e netreba vytvįra&tcaron; linky v
	adresįroch pre runlevel <constant>3/multiuser</constant>, prķpadne <constant>5/X</constant>.
        </para>

      <para>V dokumentįcii k <application>initscripts</application> sa pķ&scaron;e: <quote>Ak ulo&zcaron;ķte popis
	rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves (pou&zcaron;itķm <command>dumpkeys</command>) do sśboru
	<filename>/etc/sysconfig/console/default.kmap</filename>, zavedie sa pri &scaron;tarte systému e&scaron;te
	pred pripįjanķm/kontrolou sśborovżch systémov. To mō&zcaron;e by&tcaron; u&zcaron;ito&ccaron;né, ak potrebujete zada&tcaron;
	heslo roota v prķpade problémov. Musķ to by&tcaron; <quote>dumpnutż</quote> popis rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves
	a nie skopķrovanż sśbor z <filename class="directory">/usr/lib/kbd/keytables/</filename>,
	preto&zcaron;e tie &ccaron;asto e&scaron;te vkladajś (include) iné popisy z tejto adresįrovej
	&scaron;truktśry.</quote></para>

      <para>Po pripojenķ sśborovżch systémov, v prķpade, &zcaron;e existuje spustite&lcaron;nż sśbor
	<filename>/etc/rc.d/init.d/keytable</filename> a adresįr
	<filename class="directory">/usr/lib/kbd/keymaps/</filename>, vykonį sa prķkaz
	<screen>
sh# /etc/rc.d/init.d/keytable start
	</screen></para>
	
      <para>Tento u&zcaron; zavedie popis rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves tak, ako to mįte ur&ccaron;ené premennżmi v sśbore
	<filename>/etc/sysconfig/keyboard</filename>, preto nemusķte vytvįra&tcaron; odkazy v jednotlivżch
	<filename class="directory">rc[1-5].d/</filename> adresįroch.</para>

      <para>To, &ccaron;o sme si hovorili o zmene fontu pri prihlįsenķ nejakého u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;a na virtuįlnej
	konzole, sa dį aplikova&tcaron; aj na rozlo&zcaron;enie klįves. Śplne najjednoduch&scaron;ie rie&scaron;enie (ktoré sa
	pri prvom odhlįsenķ po&scaron;le do krķkov) je asi takéto:
	<variablelist>
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><filename>~/.bash_profile</filename>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<programlisting>
if tty 2>/dev/null |grep '/dev/tty[0-9]*$' &>/dev/null && ! [ -f ~/.keymap ]; then
	dumpkeys > ~/.keymap
	loadkeys gr.map
fi
		</programlisting></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	  
	  <varlistentry>
	    <term><filename>~/.bash_logout</filename>:</term>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		<programlisting>
if tty 2>/dev/null |grep '/dev/tty[0-9]*$' &>/dev/null && [ -f ~/.keymap ]; then
	loadkeys ~/.keymap
	rm -f ~/.keymap
fi
		</programlisting></para>
	    </listitem>
	  </varlistentry>
	</variablelist></para>
    </section> <!-- console-kbd-autoload -->
  </section> <!-- console-kbd -->
      
  <section id="console-summary">
    <title>Zhrnutie nastavenķ konzoly</title>

    <para>Pokia&lcaron; some sa niekde nesekol, tak minimįlne v distribściįch
      <systemitem class="osname">RedHat</systemitem> a
      <systemitem class="osname">Mandrake</systemitem> by po tżchto zmenįch mala do pohody za&scaron;lapa&tcaron;
      slovenskį podpora (fonty + klįvesnica).
      <variablelist>
	<varlistentry>
	  <term><filename>/etc/sysconfig/i18n</filename>:</term>
	  <listitem>
	    <variablelist>
	      <varlistentry>
		<term><application>kbd</application>:</term>
		<listitem>
		  <para>
		    <programlisting>
SYSFONT=lat2a-16
		    </programlisting></para>
		</listitem>
	      </varlistentry>
	      
	      <varlistentry>
		<term><application>console-tools</application>:</term>
		<listitem>
		  <para>
		    <programlisting>
SYSFONT=lat2u-16
SYSFONTACM=iso02
		    </programlisting></para>
		</listitem>
	      </varlistentry>
	    </variablelist>
	  </listitem>
	</varlistentry>
	
	<varlistentry>
	  <term><filename>/etc/sysconfig/keyboard</filename>:</term>
	  <listitem>
	    <para>
	      <programlisting>
KEYTABLE=sk-qwertz
KBCHARSET=iso-8859-2
	      </programlisting></para>
	  </listitem>
	</varlistentry>
      </variablelist></para>

    <para>Tie&zcaron;, ak zadįvate rootovské heslo s pou&zcaron;itķm iného rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves ako je &scaron;tandardné
      (<computeroutput>us</computeroutput>), vlo&zcaron;te si jeho popis do sśboru
      <filename>/etc/sysconfig/console/default.kmap</filename>. Pozor, nesmiete len tak skopķrova&tcaron;
      sśbor, alebo vytvori&tcaron; link! Ak chcete pou&zcaron;i&tcaron; naprķklad rozlo&zcaron;enie
      <computeroutput>sk-qwertz</computeroutput>, urobte to takto:
      <screen>
sh$ loadkeys sk-qwertz
sh# dumpkeys >/etc/sysconfig/console/default.kmap
      </screen></para>

    <para>Ak chcete nastavi&tcaron; slovenskż font a klįvesnicu len jednorazovo, tieto prķkazy by to mali
      dokįza&tcaron;:
      <variablelist>
	<varlistentry>
	  <term><application>kbd</application>:</term>
	  <listitem>
	    <para>
	      <screen>
sh$ setfont lat2a-16
sh$ loadkeys sk-qwertz
	      </screen></para>
	  </listitem>
	</varlistentry>
	
	<varlistentry>
	  <term><application>console-tools</application>:</term>
	  <listitem>
	    <para>
	      <screen>
sh$ consolechars -f lat2u-16 -m iso02
sh$ loadkeys sk-qwertz
	      </screen></para>
	  </listitem>
	</varlistentry>
      </variablelist></para>

    <para>...a naspä&tcaron; na &scaron;tandardné nastavenia:
      <variablelist>
	<varlistentry>
	  <term><application>kbd</application>:</term>
	  <listitem>
	    <para>
	      <screen>
sh$ setfont
sh$ loadkeys -d
	      </screen></para>
	  </listitem>
	</varlistentry>
	
	<varlistentry>
	  <term><application>console-tools</application>:</term>
	  <listitem>
	    <para>
	      <screen>
sh$ consolechars -d
sh$ loadkeys -d
	      </screen></para>
	  </listitem>
	</varlistentry>
      </variablelist></para>
  </section> <!-- console-summary -->
</section> <!-- console -->


<!--DOCTYPE section PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DocBook V4.1//EN"-->
<!-- $Id$ -->

<section id="xwindow">
  <title>Nastavenia X Window Systemu</title>

  <para>&Ccaron;oko&lcaron;vek sa chystįte robi&tcaron; s <application>X Window Systemom</application> a sloven&ccaron;inou
    dokopy, s&lcaron;ubujem, &zcaron;e vįm to nebude fungova&tcaron;, ak nenastavķte totok taktok:
    <programlisting>
LC_CTYPE=sk
    </programlisting></para>

  <para>&Ccaron;o to znamenį a ako sa to nastavuje, tak o tom pojednįva kapitola <xref linkend="locales"
    endterm="locales.title">.</para>

  <section id="xwindow-fonts">
    <title>Slovenské fonty v X Window Systeme</title>

    <para>Predpokladįm, &zcaron;e <application>X Window System</application> mįte nain&scaron;talovanż, prķpadne
      aj <application>X Font Server</application>, va&ccaron;&scaron;inu dōle&zcaron;itżch vecķ sme si povedali v &ccaron;asti o
      konzole, po&dcaron;me si rovno nain&scaron;talova&tcaron; slovenské fonty.</para>

    <section id="xwindow-fonts-xsinstall">
      <title>In&scaron;talįcia fontov - X server</title>

      <para>Slovenské fonty pre <acronym>X</acronym> nįjdeme v balķku
	<application>XFree86-ISO8859-2</application>, ve&lcaron;a &dcaron;al&scaron;ķch je v balķkoch
	<application>XFree-ISO8859-2-<emphasis>&lt;druh></emphasis>-fonts</application>, kde
	<emphasis>&lt;druh></emphasis> mō&zcaron;e by&tcaron; <application>Type1</application>,
	<application>100dpi</application> alebo <application>75dpi</application>. Ak chcete pou&zcaron;ķva&tcaron;
	sloven&ccaron;inu seriózne (<application>Gimp</application>, <application>Netscape</application>,
	lokalizįcia), nain&scaron;talujte si v&scaron;etky, ak potrebujete slovenskż font len napr. v
	<application>XTerme</application>, posta&ccaron;ķ vįm zįkladnż balķk.</para>

      <para>Po rozbalenķ archķvu sa fonty nachįdzajś na nieko&lcaron;kżch miestach. V&scaron;etky cesty k novżm
	fontom si treba odpisa&tcaron;, zapamäta&tcaron;, ma&tcaron; na o&ccaron;iach:
	<simplelist>
	  <member><filename class="directory">/usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/misc</filename></member>
	  <member><filename class="directory">/usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/75dpi</filename></member>
	  <member><filename class="directory">/usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/100dpi</filename></member>
	  <member><filename class="directory">/usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/Type1</filename></member>
	</simplelist></para>

      <para>Tieto cesty toti&zcaron; budeme vklada&tcaron; do konfigura&ccaron;ného sśboru <application>X Window
	Systemu</application> (<filename>/etc/X11/XF86Config</filename>, prķpadne
	<filename>/etc/X11/XF86Config-4</filename>). Tżm sprķstupnķme X serveru fonty z tżchto
	adresįrov. Sekciu <computeroutput>"Files"</computeroutput> upravķme vlo&zcaron;enķm riadkov
	<computeroutput>FontPath</computeroutput>:
	<programlisting>
Section "Files"
    ...  
    FontPath   "/usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/misc"
    FontPath   "/usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/75dpi"
    FontPath   "/usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/100dpi"
    FontPath   "/usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/Type1"
EndSection
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Sprįvne poradie riadkov s cestami k fontom nįjdete v
	<citetitle>XWindow-User-HOWTO</citetitle>, ale nemali by ste ma&tcaron; ve&lcaron;ké problémy ani ke&dcaron;
	slovenské fonty vlo&zcaron;ķte na koniec zoznamu.</para>

      <para>Za behu <application>X Window Systemu</application> pridįte nové adresįre s fontami
	prķkazom
	<screen>
sh$ xset +fp /usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/misc, /usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/75dpi, &hellip;
	</screen></para>
    </section> <!-- xwindow-fonts-xsinstall -->

    <section id="xwindow-fonts-fsinstall">
      <title>In&scaron;talįcia fontov - X Font Server</title>

      <para><application>X Font Server</application> ponśka druhż spōsob spravovania fontov pre
	<application>X Window Server</application>, a to ako pre lokįlnu ma&scaron;inu, tak aj pre
	vzdialené systémy. Moderné distribście u&zcaron; po in&scaron;talįcii ponśkajś nakonfigurovanż
	<application>X Font Server</application> a <application>X Window System</application>, ktorż
	vyu&zcaron;ķva jeho slu&zcaron;by.</para>

      <para>Pri tomto spōsobe treba cesty k fontom vlo&zcaron;i&tcaron; do konfigura&ccaron;ného sśboru
	<application>X Font Serveru</application> a konfigurįcia v
	<filename>/etc/X11/X86Config</filename> (XF86Config-4) by mala vyzera&tcaron; takto:
	<programlisting>
Section "Files"
    FontPath "unix/:7100"
EndSection
	</programlisting>
	za predpokladu, &zcaron;e X Font Server be&zcaron;ķ na porte 7100 (vo&lcaron;ba prķkazového riadku
	<computeroutput>-port</computeroutput>).</para>

      <para>Ak teda pou&zcaron;ķvate <application><acronym>xfs</acronym></application>, nie&ccaron;o podobné ako v
	predchįdzajścej kapitole urobķte s konfigura&ccaron;nżm sśborom pre tento program
	(<filename>/etc/X11/fs/config</filename>) v &ccaron;asti
	<computeroutput>catalogue</computeroutput>:
	<programlisting>
catalogue = ...,
        /usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/misc,
        /usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/75dpi,
        /usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/100dpi,
        /usr/share/fonts/ISO8859-2/Type1
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Hne&dcaron; potom musķ <application><acronym>xfs</acronym></application> znovu na&ccaron;ķta&tcaron;
	konfigura&ccaron;nż sśbor a tżm umo&zcaron;nķte pou&zcaron;ķvanie slovenskżch fontov lokįlnemu aj inżm
	<acronym>X</acronym> serverom:
	<screen>
sh# killall -USR1 xfs
	</screen></para>
    </section> <!-- xwindow-fonts-fsinstall -->
	
    <section id="xwindow-fonts-ttf">
      <title id="xwindow-fonts-ttf.title">Slovenské TrueType fonty</title>

      <para>Ak vlastnķte legįlnu kópiu systému <systemitem class="osname">WindowsXX</systemitem>
	(kde <acronym>XX</acronym> je hoci&ccaron;o), alebo <systemitem class="osname">MacOS</systemitem>,
	nemali by vįs zavrie&tcaron;, ak pou&zcaron;ijete <application>TrueType</application> fonty obsiahnuté v
	ich distribściįch. Existuje aj mnoho balķkov s <application>TrueType</application> fontmi s
	podporou normy <acronym>ISO-8859-2</acronym>, ktoré sś vo&lcaron;ne dostupné.</para>

      <para>Popis in&scaron;talįcie takżchto fontov prebehneme len v krįtkosti, podrobnej&scaron;ķ
	nįjdete v dokumentįcii k balķku <application>free-type</application>:</para>

      <procedure>
	<step>
	  <para>Skopķrujte sśbory s <application>TrueType</application> fontami napr. do adresįra
	    <filename class="directory">/usr/share/fonts/ttf/win/</filename>. Odporś&ccaron;am zmeni&tcaron;
	    menį sśborov s fontami aj ich prķpony na malé pķsmenį -- mal some s tżm
	    problémy.</para>
	</step>

	<step>
	  <para>Vytvorte v ka&zcaron;dom adresįri sśbor s informįciami o scalable fontoch
	    <filename>fonts.scale</filename> nasledovnżm prķkazom:
	    <screen>
sh# cd /usr/share/fonts/ttf/win
sh# ttmkfdir -o fonts.scale
	    </screen></para>

	  <para>Ak to nie je celkom ono a dostanete ve&lcaron;a chybovżch hlįsenķ, alebo sśbor
	    <filename>fonts.scale</filename> obsahuje prķli&scaron; mįlo zįznamov o fontoch v adresįri,
	    skśste pou&zcaron;i&tcaron; s prķkazom <command>ttmkfdir</command> aj vo&lcaron;bu prķkazoveho riadku
	    <computeroutput>-c</computeroutput>.</para>
	</step>

	<step>
	  <para>Zoznam fontov v sśbore, ktorż na&ccaron;ķtava <acronym>X</acronym> server aj
	    <application>xfs</application>, vytvorķte nasledovne:
	    <screen>
sh# cd /usr/share/fonts/ttf/win
sh# mkfontdir
	    </screen></para>
	</step>
      </procedure>

      <para>Od tohto momentu pokra&ccaron;ujte &scaron;tandardnżm spōsobom tak, ako je to popķsané
	v predchįdzajścej &ccaron;asti o konfigurįcii <acronym>X</acronym> servera alebo
	<application>xfs</application>.</para>
    </section> <!-- xwindow-fonts-ttf -->

    <section id="xwindow-fonts-alias">
      <title>&Ccaron;o je iné so slovenskżmi fontami</title>

      <para>Okrem toho, &zcaron;e sa slovenské znaky zobrazujś sprįvne, ni&ccaron;. Fonty z balķkov pre normu
	<acronym>ISO-8859-2</acronym> sa sķce volajś inak, ale vzh&lcaron;adom zodpovedajś &scaron;tandardnżm
	fontom. V nasledujścej tabu&lcaron;ke sś uvedené zodpovedajśce dvojice fontov:
	<table>
	  <title>Slovenské ekvivalenty &scaron;tandardnżch fontov</title>
	  <tgroup cols="2">
	    <thead>
	      <row>
		<entry>&scaron;tandardne</entry>
		<entry>iso8859-2</entry>
	      </row>
	    </thead>

	    <tbody>
	      <row>
		<entry>Times</entry>
		<entry>Kathimerini</entry>
	      </row>

	      <row>
		<entry>Helvetica</entry>
		<entry>Aplos</entry>
	      </row>

	      <row>
		<entry>New Century Schoolbook</entry>
		<entry>Anagnostiko</entry>
	      </row>

	      <row>
		<entry>Lucida</entry>
		<entry>Fotinos</entry>
	      </row>

	      <row>
		<entry>Utopia</entry>
		<entry>Chimera</entry>
	      </row>

	      <row>
		<entry>Charter</entry>
		<entry>Chartis</entry>
	      </row>
	    </tbody>
	  </tgroup>
	</table></para>

      <para>Berte tśto tabu&lcaron;ku len ako informatķvny śdaj, ktorż pravdepodobne nikdy nebudete
	potrebova&tcaron; v&dcaron;aka sśborom <filename>fonts.alias</filename> v adresįroch so slovenskżmi
	fontmi. Tie zabezpe&ccaron;ujś nahrįdzanie mien &scaron;tandardnżch fontov s uvedenou normou
	<acronym>ISO-8859-2</acronym> zodpovedajścimi menami slovenskżch fontov. Naprķklad
	po&zcaron;iadavka na font
	<literallayout><computeroutput>
-b&amp;h-lucida-bold-i-normal-sans-11-80-100-100-p-69-iso8859-2
	</computeroutput></literallayout>
	poskytne a teda zobrazķ v skuto&ccaron;nosti font
	<literallayout><computeroutput>
-biznet-fotinos-bold-i-normal-sans-11-80-100-100-p-69-iso8859-2
	</computeroutput></literallayout></para>
    </section> <!-- xwindow-fonts-alias -->

    <section id="xwindow-fonts-tshooting">
      <title>Strie&lcaron;anie ta&zcaron;kostķ</title>

      <para>Ak budete dostįva&tcaron; po spustenķ <acronym>X</acronym> serveru chybové hlįsenia typu
	<quote><computeroutput>Can't open default font 'fixed'</computeroutput></quote> alebo
	<quote><computeroutput>unable to open font ...</computeroutput></quote>, alebo vįm
	jednoducho nie&ccaron;o spojené s fontami pod iXami bude kazi&tcaron; nįladu, uistite sa, &zcaron;e mįte v
	poriadku nasledovné veci.</para>
      
      <orderedlist>
	<listitem>
	  <para>V&scaron;etky adresįre s fontami, samotné sśbory fontov a sśbory, ktoré &ccaron;ķta <application>X
	    Window System</application> alebo <application>X Font Server</application>, musia ma&tcaron;
	    nastavené rozumné prķstupové prįva.</para>
	</listitem>
	    
	<listitem>
	  <para>V adresįroch, v ktorżch sa nachįdzajś fonty, musķ existova&tcaron; sśbor
	    <filename>fonts.dir</filename>. Ak nie, spustite v tżchto adresįroch program
	    <command>mkfontdir</command>. V adresįroch s <application>TrueType</application> fontmi
	    musķte e&scaron;te predtżm vytvori&tcaron; sśbor <filename>fonts.scale</filename> tak ako je to
	    popķsane v &ccaron;asti
	    <xref linkend="xwindow-fonts-ttf" endterm="xwindow-fonts-ttf.title">.</para>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <para>Ak idete bez <command>xfs</command>, naozaj v&scaron;etky adresįre s fontami musia
	    by&tcaron; uvedené v sśbore <filename>XF86Config</filename>.</para>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <para>V prķpade, ze pou&zcaron;ķvate <command>xfs</command>, tieto adresįre musia by&tcaron; uvedené v
	    sśbore <filename>/etc/X11/fs/config</filename>. Navy&scaron;e, xfs musķ be&zcaron;a&tcaron; na nejakom porte
	    (napr.  7100) a v <filename>XF86Config</filename> musķ by&tcaron; cesta k fontom uvedenį ako
	    adresa s &ccaron;ķslom toho portu, asi takto:
	    <programlisting>
FontPath "unix/:7100"
	    </programlisting></para>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <para>Po zmenįch v konfigura&ccaron;nżch sśboroch <application>X Window Systemu</application>
	    alebo <application>X Font Serveru</application> je nutnż re&scaron;tart alebo znovuna&ccaron;ķtanie
	    nastavenķ:
	    <variablelist>
	      <varlistentry>
		<term><application>X Window System</application></term>
		<listitem>
		  <screen>
sh$ xset fp rehash
		  </screen>
		</listitem>
	      </varlistentry>

	      <varlistentry>
		<term><application>X Font Server</application></term>
		<listitem>
		  <screen>
sh# killall -USR1 xfs
		  </screen>
		</listitem>
	      </varlistentry>
	    </variablelist></para>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <para>Ak mįte v <filename>inittabe</filename> nastavené spś&scaron;&tcaron;anie X serveru pri &scaron;tarte
	    systému (runlevel <constant>5/X</constant>), rad&scaron;ej si to pri pokusoch s fontami zme&ncaron;te
	    na <constant>3/multiuser</constant> a&zcaron; pokia&lcaron; si nie ste sakramentsky istķ, &zcaron;e X server
	    pri &scaron;tarte nįjde fonty.  Ak to neurobķte a nastavenia budś nesprįvne, za&ccaron;nś sa dia&tcaron;
	    zįhadné veci typu <quote>X server sa skon&ccaron;ķ, lebo nenįjde fonty ale init ho znovu spustķ
	    a ten nenįjde fonty, tak sa skon&ccaron;ķ, ale init ho...</quote>. Znakom toho je hlį&scaron;ka
	    <computeroutput>INIT: Id "x" respawning too fast: disabled for 5
	    minutes</computeroutput>.</para>
	</listitem>

	<listitem>
	  <para><application>X Window System</application> h&lcaron;adį (pre normįlneho u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;a)
	    konfigura&ccaron;né sśbory v tomto poradķ:
	    <simplelist>
	      <member><filename>/etc/X11/&lt;cmdline></filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/usr/X11R6/etc/X11/&lt;cmdline></filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/etc/X11/$XF86CONFIG</filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/usr/X11R6/etc/X11/$XF86CONFIG</filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/etc/X11/XF86Config-4</filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/etc/X11/XF86Config</filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/etc/XF86Config</filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/usr/X11R6/etc/X11/XF86Config.&lt;hostname></filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/usr/X11R6/etc/X11/XF86Config-4</filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/usr/X11R6/etc/X11/XF86Config</filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/usr/X11R6/lib/X11/XF86Config.&lt;hostname></filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/usr/X11R6/lib/X11/XF86Config-4</filename></member>
	      <member><filename>/usr/X11R6/lib/X11/XF86Config</filename></member>
	    </simplelist></para>

	  <para>Pamätajte na to pri editovanķ konfigurįkov a v&zcaron;dy sa uistite, &ccaron;i neexistuje sśbor,
	    ktorż je v tomto zozname vy&scaron;&scaron;ie, ako ten, ktorż editujete.</para>
	</listitem>
      </orderedlist>
    </section> <!-- xwindow-fonts-tshooting -->
  </section> <!-- xwindow-fonts -->
  
  <section id="xwindow-kbd">
    <title>Slovenskį klįvesnica v X Window Systeme</title>

    <para>Skōr jak to tu celé rozto&ccaron;ķme, zadajte prķkaz
      <screen>
sh$ rpm -q XFree86
      </screen></para>

    <para>V&scaron;etky tie &ccaron;ķsla za <computeroutput>XFree86</computeroutput>, &ccaron;o vįm tento prķkaz vypķ&scaron;e,
      udįvajś verziu vį&scaron;ho <application>XFree86 X Window Systemu</application>.</para>

    <para>Existuje presne &scaron;tyridsa&tcaron;dva dōvodov, pre&ccaron;o prejs&tcaron; na <application>XFree86</application>
      verziu 3.2 alebo vy&scaron;&scaron;iu, a len dva, pre&ccaron;o zosta&tcaron; pri star&scaron;ej verzii.  <systemitem
      class="osname">Red Hat Linux 6.0</systemitem> obsahuje <application>XFree86 </application>,
      verziu 3.3.3 a <systemitem class="osname">Linux Mandrake 7.0</systemitem> u&zcaron; verziu
      3.3.6.</para>

    <para>Pokia&lcaron; ste svoj opera&ccaron;nż systém nezdedili po starżch rodi&ccaron;och, je vysoko pravdepodobné, &zcaron;e
      mįte verziu <application>XFree86</application> vy&scaron;&scaron;iu ako 3.2. Inak ste naozaj krok pozadu a
      na adrese <ulink url="ftp://ftp.xfree86.org">ftp://ftp.xfree86.org</ulink> nįjdete to, &ccaron;o
      treba.</para>

    <para>Ak aj po predchįdzajścich slovįch, upozorneniach a odporś&ccaron;aniach odmietate upgrade na
      verziu 3.2, dr&zcaron;te sa nasledujścich krokov:</para>

    <procedure>
      <step>
	<para>Ak mįte <citetitle>Slovak-HOWTO</citetitle> vytla&ccaron;ené na papieri, uchopte tento do
	  &lcaron;avej ruky (ak ste &lcaron;avįk, robte v&scaron;etko naopak), zapa&lcaron;ova&ccaron; do pravej, zachovavajte
	  dostato&ccaron;nś vzdialenos&tcaron; od inżch zįpalnżch materiįlov a nekompromisne konajte.</para>
      </step>

      <step>
	<para>V prķpade, &zcaron;e mįte tento sśbor ulo&zcaron;enż niekde na disku, prķkazom 
	  <screen>
sh$ su -c'rm -fr /'
	  </screen>
	  sa ho do nieko&lcaron;kżch minśt po zadanķ hesla zaru&ccaron;ene zbavķte.</para>
      </step>
    </procedure>

    <section id="xwindow-kbd-config">
      <title>Konfigurįcia klįvesnice</title>

      <para><application>XFree86</application> 3.2 a nov&scaron;ie u&zcaron; majś tzv.
	<emphasis>XKEYBOARD</emphasis> roz&scaron;ķrenie, ktoré zjednodu&scaron;uje konfigurįciu klįvesnice pre
	<application>X Window System</application>. Teoreticky netreba urobi&tcaron; viac ako v sśbore
	<filename>/etc/X11/XF86Config</filename> vlo&zcaron;i&tcaron; do sekcie
	<computeroutput>"Keyboard"</computeroutput> nie&ccaron;o takéto:
	<programlisting>
Section "Keyboard"
    ...
    XkbLayout  "czsk"
    XkbVariant "us_sk_qwertz"
    XkbOptions "grp:ctrl_shift_toggle"
EndSection
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Ak u&zcaron; ste nebodaj u&zcaron;ķvate&lcaron;om <application>XFree86</application> verzie 4.0.0 alebo
	vy&scaron;&scaron;ej, vlo&zcaron;te do sśboru <filename>/etc/X11/XF86Config-4</filename> toto:
	<programlisting>
Section "InputDevice"
    ...
    Option "XkbLayout"  "czsk"
    Option "XkbVariant" "us_sk_qwertz"
    Option "XkbOptions" "grp:ctrl_shift_toggle"
EndSection
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Riadok v konfigura&ccaron;nom sśbore
	<programlisting>
XkbLayout "czsk"
	</programlisting>
	prķpadne pre verziu &ge; 4
	<programlisting>
Option "XkbLayout"  "czsk"
	</programlisting>
	hovorķ asi to&lcaron;ko, aby <acronym>X</acronym> server pou&zcaron;il popis rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves ulo&zcaron;enż v
	sśbore <filename>czsk</filename>. Tento a ostatné sśbory s <acronym>XKB</acronym> keymapami
	sa nachįdzajś v adresįri <filename class="directory">/usr/X11R6/lib/X11/xkb/symbols/
	</filename>.</para>

      <para>Bli&zcaron;&scaron;ie si o formįte tżchto sśborov povieme neskōr, teraz si len otvorte
	sśbor <filename>czsk</filename> a pozrite si jeho &scaron;truktśru -- hlavne &ccaron;asti
	<computeroutput>xkb_symbols</computeroutput>. Pre sloven&ccaron;inu sś dōle&zcaron;ité tieto varianty:
	<simplelist>
	  <member><computeroutput>us_sk_qwerty</computeroutput></member>
	  <member><computeroutput>us_sk_qwertz</computeroutput></member>
	  <member><computeroutput>us_sk_prog</computeroutput></member>
	  <member><computeroutput>sk_us_qwerty</computeroutput></member>
	  <member><computeroutput>sk_us_qwertz</computeroutput></member>
	  <member><computeroutput>sk_us_prog</computeroutput></member>
        </simplelist></para>
	
      <para>Niektorż z tżchto re&tcaron;azcov dosa&dcaron;te do riadku
	<programlisting>
XkbVariant "..."
	</programlisting>
	pre star&scaron;ie verzie <application>X Window Systemu</application>, alebo
	<programlisting>
Option "XkbVariant" "..."
	</programlisting>
	v konfigura&ccaron;nom sśbore pre <acronym>X</acronym> sever verzia 4.</para>

      <para>Varianty <computeroutput>us_sk_qwerty</computeroutput> a
	<computeroutput>sk_us_qwerty</computeroutput> sś prakticky toto&zcaron;né, jedinż rozdiel je v tom,
	ktoré rozlo&zcaron;enie klįves bude nastavené po &scaron;tarte <application>X Window
	Systemu</application>. Pre <computeroutput>sk_us_*</computeroutput> je to slovenské, pre
	<computeroutput>us_sk_*</computeroutput> zase americké.</para>

      <para>Prepķna&tcaron; medzi slovenskżm a americkżm rozlo&zcaron;enķm klįves mo&zcaron;no klįvesom
	<keycap>Scroll Lock</keycap>, prķpadne aj inżmi, ak vlo&zcaron;ķte do konfigurįcie klįvesnice
	riadok:
	<screen>
Options "grp:..."
	</screen>
	alebo pre <application>X Window System</application> verzie 4.0 alebo nov&scaron;ķ:
	<screen>
Option "XkbOptions" "grp:..."
	</screen></para>

      <para>&Ccaron;as&tcaron; <computeroutput>grp:&hellip;</computeroutput> nahra&dcaron;te niektorou z nasledujścich
	mo&zcaron;nostķ a mō&zcaron;ete prepķna&tcaron; rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves pomocou danej klįvesovej skratky:
	<table>
	  <title>Mo&zcaron;nosti prepķnania medzi rozlo&zcaron;eniami klįves</title>
	  <tgroup cols="2">
	    <thead>
	      <row>
		<entry>vo&lcaron;ba</entry>
		<entry>prepķnanie medzi rozlo&zcaron;eniami</entry>
	      </row>
	    </thead>

	    <tbody>
	      <row>
		<entry>grp:ctrl_shift_toggle</entry>
		<entry>LShift + LCtrl / RShift + RCtrl</entry>
	      </row>

	      <row>
		<entry>grp:caps_toggle</entry>
		<entry>Caps Lock / LShift + RShift</entry>
	      </row>

	      <row>
		<entry>grp:ctrl_alt_toggle</entry>
		<entry>Ctrl + Alt</entry>
	      </row>
	    </tbody>
	  </tgroup>
        </table></para>

      <para>Pri nastavovanķ alternatķvnych klįvesovżch kombinįciķ na prepķnanie medzi rozlo&zcaron;eniami
	klįves si dįvajte pozor, aby dané nastavenie nekolidovalo s u&zcaron; existujścimi klįvesovżmi
	skratkami (naprķklad vį&scaron;ho mana&zcaron;éra okien). Naprķklad pri nastavenom
	<computeroutput>ctrl_alt_toggle</computeroutput> nefunguje <keycombo> <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
	<keycap>Alt</keycap> <keycap>Backspace</keycap> </keycombo> (<foreignphrase>Kill X
	Server</foreignphrase>).</para>
    </section> <!-- xwindow-kbd-config -->

    <section id="xwindow-kbd-keymap">
      <title>XKB keymapy</title>

      <para><application>X Window System</application> umo&zcaron;&ncaron;uje definova&tcaron; vlastné popisy rozlo&zcaron;enia
	klįves prakticky pre akżko&lcaron;vek jazyk. Na to slś&zcaron;ia keymap sśbory -- nie&ccaron;o ve&lcaron;mi podobné tżm
	keymap sśborom, o ktorżch sme hovorili v &ccaron;asti o nastaveniach konzoly. Formįt keymap sśborov
	pre <application>X Window System</application> dovo&lcaron;uje vytvįrat sśbory s jednoduchżm
	popisom len &ccaron;asti klįvesnice, ale aj zlo&zcaron;ité sśbory s mnohżmi rozlo&zcaron;eniami.</para>

      <para>Naozaj nemį zmysel podrobne popisova&tcaron; mo&zcaron;nosti <acronym>XKB</acronym> keymap sśborov,
	snį&dcaron; budś sta&ccaron;i&tcaron; len śplné zįklady, ktoré vįm dovolia robi&tcaron; malé zmeny v u&zcaron; existujucich
	popisoch rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves. Podstatne viac o tżchto sśboroch sa dozviete, ke&dcaron; si ich sami
	pozriete a poskś&scaron;ate.</para>

      <para>V XKB popisoch rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves majś riadky takżto formįt:
	<programlisting>
key &lt;TLDE> { [ quoteleft, asciitilde ], [ semicolon, degree ] };
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>K&lcaron;ś&ccaron;ové slovo key ozna&ccaron;uje za&ccaron;iatok definķcie znaku, ktorého kód nasleduje uzavretż v
	<computeroutput>&lt;</computeroutput>&nbsp;a&nbsp;<computeroutput>></computeroutput>, celį
	definicia je uzavretį v krśtenżch zįtvorkįch a dvojice znakov pre ka&zcaron;dś skupinu
	(<foreignphrase>Group</foreignphrase>) sa uzavierajś do hranatżch zįtvoriek. Skupiny mō&zcaron;u
	by&tcaron; definované naprķklad takto:
	<programlisting>
name[Group1] = "US/ASCII";
name[Group2] = "Slovak";
	</programlisting></para>

      <para>Potom prvé dva znaky (<computeroutput>quoteleft</computeroutput> a <computeroutput>
	asciitilde</computeroutput>) v definķcii znaku platia pre prvś skupinu (<computeroutput>
	US/ASCII</computeroutput>) a druhé dva (<computeroutput>semicolon</computeroutput> a
	<computeroutput>degree</computeroutput>) pre druhś skupinu
	(<computeroutput>Slovak</computeroutput>).</para>

      <para>Kódy jednotlivżch klįvesov &lcaron;ahko zistķte z keymap sśborov, ktorżch je v adresįri
	<filename class="directory">/usr/X11R6/lib/X11/xkb/symbols/</filename> naozaj dos&tcaron;, takisto,
	nįzvy znakov a m&racute;tvych klįves sa ve&lcaron;mi nelķ&scaron;ia od tżch, ktoré platia v keymap sśboroch pre
	textovś konzolu. No a nakoniec, v prķlohe <xref linkend="xwindow-examples-keymap"
	endterm="xwindow-examples-keymap.title"> nįjdete jeden vzorovż prķklad slovenského
	rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves pre <application>X Window System</application>.</para>
    </section> <!-- xwindow-kbd-keymap -->
  </section> <!-- xwindow-kbd -->

  <section id="xwindow-mouse">
    <title>Slovenskį my&scaron; v X Window Systeme</title>

    <para>Mimoriadne zlo&zcaron;ité bolo do verzie 4.0.1 nastavovanie sloven&ccaron;iny pre my&scaron;.  Na&scaron;tastie,
      vżvojįri si spomenuli, &zcaron;e i toto zariadenie a jeho ovlįda&ccaron;e by mali v plnej miere podporova&tcaron;
      miestne nastavenia tak, ako je to naprķklad u klįvesnice. Dokonca sa objavili pokusy
      lokalizova&tcaron; tablety a svetelné perį.</para>

    <para>V predchįdzajścich verziįch <application>X Window Systemu</application> bola tįto podpora
      ve&lcaron;mi slabo implementovanį a len nieko&lcaron;kżm nįrodnostiam sa podarilo rozchodi&tcaron; my&scaron; vo svojom
      jazyku.  Slovenskķ pou&zcaron;ķvatelia museli na svojich my&scaron;iach robi&tcaron; rōzne śpravy od tupķrovania
      &scaron;nśry a&zcaron; po kastrįciu, ale vżsledky boli aj tak neuspokojivé.</para>

    <para>Popķ&scaron;eme si teraz v krįtkosti postup posloven&ccaron;ovania my&scaron;i v <application>X Window
      Systeme</application>, verzia 4.0.1 a vy&scaron;&scaron;ie:</para>

    <procedure>
      <step>
	<para>Odpojte svoju my&scaron; od po&ccaron;ķta&ccaron;a, poutierajte a vyle&scaron;tite jej gu&lcaron;u, skontrolujte
	  mikrotla&ccaron;idlį a celkovo ju o&scaron;etrite. Odlo&zcaron;te ju do tepla a sucha.  Dōle&zcaron;ité je aspo&ncaron; raz
	  za de&ncaron; k nej pristśpi&tcaron; s <citetitle>Pravidlami slovenského pravopisu</citetitle> a
	  prķjemnżm hlasom pred&ccaron;ķtava&tcaron; slovį zo slovnķka. Po pįr ty&zcaron;d&ncaron;och mō&zcaron;ete prejs&tcaron; k
	  jednoduchej beletrii a rozprįvkam.</para>
      </step>

      <step>
	<para>Po&ccaron;as tohto obdobia odvykania my&scaron;i od cudzķch jazykov nain&scaron;talujte slovenské fonty a
	  rozlo&zcaron;enie klįves. Takisto sa pokśste pozhį&ncaron;a&tcaron; slovenské preklady ob&lcaron;śbenżch aplikįciķ
	  va&scaron;ej my&scaron;i. Ako pozadie obrazovky odporś&ccaron;am nastavi&tcaron; slovenskś zįstavu a adresįre s
	  hudbou by ste mali obohati&tcaron; o tituly ako Iné Kafe, Maduar a rōzne iné rockové uragįny a
	  punkové smr&scaron;te.</para>
      </step>

      <step>
	<para>Ak mįte pocit, &zcaron;e my&scaron; je pripravenį vstśpi&tcaron; do &ccaron;isto slovenského prostredia va&scaron;ich
	  iXov, opatrne ju pripojte a poukazujte jej v&scaron;etky zįkutia jej vynoveného domova.</para>
      </step>
    </procedure>
      
    <para>E&scaron;te by some rįd pripomenul, &zcaron;e nie v&scaron;etky my&scaron;i sś rovnako odolné vo&ccaron;i zmenįm nįrodného
      prostredia a preto sa v&zcaron;dy pri kśpe my&scaron;i informujte na mo&zcaron;nosti posloven&ccaron;ovania toho ktorého
      vżrobku.</para>
  </section> <!-- xwindow-mouse -->

  <section id="xwindow-examples">
    <title>Prķklady</title>

    <section id="xwindow-examples-xf86config">
      <title>XF86Config-4</title>

      <para>&Ccaron;as&tcaron; konfigura&ccaron;ného sśboru X Window Systemu (4.0.1) s rozbehanżm X Font Serverom,
	slovenskżm rozlo&zcaron;enķm klįves s prepķnanķm medzi americkżm a slovenskżm pomocou Shift + Ctrl.
	<programlisting>
Section "Files"
    RgbPath     "/usr/X11R6/lib/X11/rgb"
    FontPath    "unix/:7100"
    ModulePath  "/usr/X11R6/lib/modules"
EndSection

Section "InputDevice"
    Identifier	"Keyboard1"
    Driver	"Keyboard"
    Option "AutoRepeat" "500 30"
    Option "XkbRules"	"xfree86"
    Option "XkbModel"	"pc104"
    Option "XkbLayout"	"czsk"
    Option "XkbVariant" "us_sk_qwertz"
    Option "XkbOptions" "grp:ctrl_shift_toggle"
EndSection
	</programlisting></para>
    </section> <!-- xwindow-examples-xf86config -->

    <section id="xwindow-examples-keymap">
      <title id="xwindow-examples-keymap.title">XKB keymap</title>

      <para>Prķklad śplne jednoduchého popisu rozlo&zcaron;enia klįves pre sloven&ccaron;inu:
	<programlisting>
partial default alphanumeric_keys
xkb_symbols "sk_us" {

    name[Group1] = "Slovak";
    name[Group2] = "US/ASCII";

// line 1
    key &lt;TLDE> {     [       semicolon,      degree          ],
                     [       quoteleft,      asciitilde      ]       };
    key &lt;AE01> {     [            plus,      1               ],
                     [               1,      exclam          ]       };
    key &lt;AE02> {     [          lcaron,      2               ],
                     [               2,      at              ]       };
    key &lt;AE03> {     [          scaron,      3               ],
                     [               3,      numbersign      ]       };
    key &lt;AE04> {     [          ccaron,      4               ],
                     [               4,      dollar          ]       };
    key &lt;AE05> {     [          tcaron,      5               ],
                     [               5,      percent         ]       };
    key &lt;AE06> {     [          zcaron,      6               ],
                     [               6,      asciicircum     ]       };
    key &lt;AE07> {     [          yacute,      7               ],
                     [               7,      ampersand       ]       };
    key &lt;AE08> {     [          aacute,      8               ],
                     [               8,      asterisk        ]       };
    key &lt;AE09> {     [          iacute,      9               ],
                     [               9,      parenleft       ]       };
    key &lt;AE10> {     [          eacute,      0               ],
                     [               0,      parenright      ]       };
    key &lt;AE11> {     [           equal,      percent         ],
                     [           minus,      underscore      ]       };
    key &lt;AE12> {     [      dead_acute,      dead_caron      ],
                     [           equal,      plus            ]       };

// line 2
    key &lt;AD01> {     [               q,      Q               ],
                     [               q,      Q               ]       };
    key &lt;AD02> {     [               w,      W               ],
                     [               w,      W               ]       };
    key &lt;AD03> {     [               e,      E               ],
                     [               e,      E               ]       };
    key &lt;AD04> {     [               r,      R               ],
                     [               r,      R               ]       };
    key &lt;AD05> {     [               t,      T               ],
                     [               t,      T               ]       };
    key &lt;AD06> {     [               z,      Z               ],
                     [               y,      Y               ]       };
    key &lt;AD07> {     [               u,      U               ],
                     [               u,      U               ]       };
    key &lt;AD08> {     [               i,      I               ],
                     [               i,      I               ]       };
    key &lt;AD09> {     [               o,      O               ],
                     [               o,      O               ]       };
    key &lt;AD10> {     [               p,      P               ],
                     [               p,      P               ]       };
    key &lt;AD11> {     [          uacute,      slash           ],
                     [     bracketleft,      braceleft       ]       };
    key &lt;AD12> {     [      adiaeresis,      parenleft       ],
                     [    bracketright,      braceright      ]       };

// line 3
    key &lt;AC02> {     [               s,      S               ],
                     [               s,      S               ]       };
    key &lt;AC03> {     [               d,      D               ],
                     [               d,      D               ]       };
    key &lt;AC04> {     [               f,      F               ],
                     [               f,      F               ]       };
    key &lt;AC05> {     [               g,      G               ],
                     [               g,      G               ]       };
    key &lt;AC08> {     [               k,      K               ],
                     [               k,      K               ]       };
    key &lt;AC09> {     [               l,      L               ],
                     [               l,      L               ]       };
    key &lt;AC10> {     [     ocircumflex,      quotedbl        ],
                     [       semicolon,      colon           ]       };
    key &lt;AC11> {     [         section,      exclam          ],
                     [      quoteright,      quotedbl        ]       };

// line 4
    key &lt;AB01> {     [               y,      Y               ],
                     [               z,      Z               ]       };
    key &lt;AB02> {     [               x,      X               ],
                     [               x,      X               ]       };
    key &lt;AB04> {     [               v,      V               ],
                     [               v,      V               ]       };
    key &lt;AB05> {     [               b,      B               ],
                     [               b,      B               ]       };
    key &lt;AB06> {     [               n,      N               ],
                     [               n,      N               ]       };
    key &lt;AB07> {     [               m,      M               ],
                     [               m,      M               ]       };
    key &lt;AB08> {     [           comma,      question        ],
                     [           comma,      less            ]       };
    key &lt;AB09> {     [          period,      colon           ],
                     [          period,      greater         ]       };
    key &lt;AB10> {     [           minus,      underscore      ],
                     [           slash,      question        ]       };
    key &lt;BKSL> {     [          ncaron,      parenright      ],
                     [       backslash,      bar             ]       };
// End alphanumeric section

// begin modifier mappings
    modifier_map Shift  { Shift_L };
    modifier_map Lock   { Caps_Lock };
    modifier_map Control{ Control_L };
    modifier_map Mod3   { Mode_switch };
};
	</programlisting></para>
    </section> <!-- xwindow-examples-keymap -->
  </section> <!-- xwindow-examples -->
</section> <!-- xwindow -->

  
<!--DOCTYPE section PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DocBook V4.1//EN"-->
<!-- $Id$ -->

<section id="kernel">
  <title>Sloven&ccaron;ina a linuxovż kernel</title>
  
  <section id="kernel-kmap">
    <title>Kompilįcia kernelu so slovenskou klįvesnicou</title>

    <para>Je ve&lcaron;mi jednoduché zmeni&tcaron; rozlo&zcaron;enie klįves, s ktorżm bude jadro vį&scaron;ho opera&ccaron;ného systému
      skompilované. Ak pou&zcaron;ijete program <command>loadkeys</command> s vo&lcaron;bou prķkazového riadku
      <computeroutput>--mktable &lt;keymapfile></computeroutput>, tento vįm vygeneruje
      <quote>zdrojovż kód</quote> sśboru <filename>&lt;keymapfile></filename>. Ten ulo&zcaron;te do sśboru
      <filename>drivers/char/defkeymap.c</filename> v adresįrovej &scaron;truktśre zdrojového kódu
      <systemitem class="osname">Linuxu</systemitem>.
      <screen>
sh# cd /usr/src/linux
sh# loadkeys --mktable sk-qwerty > drivers/char/defkeymap.c
      </screen></para>

    <para>Toto je akįsi nįhrada za <filename>/etc/sysconfig/console/default.kmap</filename> s tżm
      rozdielom, &zcaron;e va&scaron;e rozlo&zcaron;enie bude zavedené u&zcaron; od śplného &scaron;tartu systému. V prķpade
      problémov s initscriptami (alebo &scaron;tarte zo zįchrannej diskety) budete ma&tcaron; zavedené svoje
      rozlo&zcaron;enie v ka&zcaron;dom prķpade. Pozor, nekompilujte si kernel so slovenskżm rozlo&zcaron;enķm len preto,
      &zcaron;e &zcaron;ijete na Slovensku! Na to slś&zcaron;i prķkaz <command>loadkeys</command>. Pou&zcaron;ite toto rie&scaron;enie,
      len ak bezpodmiene&ccaron;ne potrebujete slovenské rozlo&zcaron;enie pri zadįvanķ rootovho hesla alebo tak
      podobne.</para>
  </section> <!-- kernel-kmap -->

  <section id="kernel-fat">
    <title>Diakritika v nįzvoch sśborov na FAT partķciįch</title>

    <para>Ak chcete pristupova&tcaron; spod <systemitem class="osname">Linuxu</systemitem> na
      <acronym>FAT</acronym>/<acronym>VFAT</acronym> oddiely a ma&tcaron; prķpadnś diakritiku v nįzvoch
      sśborov na takżchto partķciįch, pri konfigurįcii kernelu (pred kompilovanķm) zvo&lcaron;te tieto
      nastavenia v &ccaron;asti <menuchoice> <guimenu>Filesystems</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Native Language
      Support</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>:
      <simplelist>
        <member><systemitem class="macro">CONFIG_NLS_CODEPAGE_852</systemitem>  ---  Codepage 852
	  </member>
	
	<member><systemitem class="macro">CONFIG_NLS_ISO8859_2</systemitem>  ---  ISO 8859-2
	  (Latin 2)</member>
      </simplelist></para>

    <para>Pri pripįjanķ <acronym>FAT</acronym>/<acronym>VFAT</acronym> mō&zcaron;ete potom uvies&tcaron; vo&lcaron;bu
      <computeroutput>codepage=852</computeroutput>.</para>

    <para>Vo&lcaron;ba <computeroutput>codepage</computeroutput> nastavuje kódovś strįnku pre prevod znakov
      krįtkych mien na sśborovżch systémoch <acronym>FAT</acronym> a <acronym>VFAT</acronym>.
      Implicitne mį codepage hodnotu 437.</para>
  </section> <!-- kernel-fat -->
</section> <!-- kernel -->
 

